00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:34.000
Moyers: I'M BILL MOYERS.

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:36.000
WELCOME TO THIS SPECIAL EDITION

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.000
OF THE JOURNAL ON AIR AND ON

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:39.000
LINE.

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:40.000
FOUR YEARS AGO THE BUSH

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:41.000
ADMINISTRATION TOOK LEAVE OF

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:43.000
REALITY AND PLUNGED OUR COUNTRY

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:44.000
INTO A WAR SO POORLY PLANNED IT

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:46.000
SOON TURNED INTO A DISASTER.

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:48.000
THE STORY OF HOW HIGH OFFICIALS

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:49.000
MISLED THE COUNTRY HAS BEEN

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:51.000
TOLD, BUT THEY COULDN'T HAVE

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:53.000
DONE IT ON THEIR OWN.

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:55.000
THEY NEEDED A COMPLIANT PRESS,

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:56.000
TO PASS ON THEIR PROPAGANDA AS

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:58.000
NEWS AND CHEER THEM ON.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:00.000
SINCE THEN THOUSANDS OF PEOPLE

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:01.000
HAVE DIED, AND MORE ARE DYING TO

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:03.000
THIS DAY.

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:06.000
YET THE STORY OF HOW THE MEDIA

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:07.000
BOUGHT WHAT THE WHITE HOUSE WAS

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:08.000
SELLING HAS NOT BEEN TOLD IN

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:10.000
DEPTH ON TELEVISION.

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:12.000
AS THE WAR RAGES INTO ITS FIFTH

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:13.000
YEAR, WE LOOK BACK AT THOSE

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:15.000
MONTHS LEADING UP TO THE

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:17.000
INVASION, WHEN OUR PRESS LARGELY

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:18.000
SURRENDERED ITS INDEPENDENCE AND

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:20.000
SKEPTICISM TO JOIN WITH OUR

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:22.000
GOVERNMENT IN MARCHING TO WAR.

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:24.000
OUR REPORT WAS PRODUCED AND

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:25.000
DIRECTED BY KATHLEEN HUGHES AND

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:30.000
EDITED BY ALISON AMRON.

00:02:13.000 --> 00:02:15.000
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN, THE

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:18.000
PRESIDENT OF THE UNITED STATES.

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:20.000
GOOD EVENING, I'M PLEASED TO

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:22.000
TAKE YOUR QUESTIONS TONIGHT.

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:23.000
Moyers: TWO WEEKS BEFORE HE

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:25.000
WILL ORDER AMERICA TO WAR,

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:26.000
PRESIDENT BUSH CALLS A PRESS

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:27.000
CONFERENCE TO MAKE THE CASE FOR

00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:29.000
DISARMING SADDAM HUSSEIN.

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:31.000
IRAQ IS A PART OF THE WAR ON

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:32.000
TERROR.

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:33.000
IT'S A COUNTRY THAT TRAINS

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:34.000
TERRORISTS, IT'S A COUNTRY THAT

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:36.000
CAN ARM TERRORISTS.

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:37.000
SADDAM HUSSEIN AND HIS WEAPONS

00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:39.000
ARE A DIRECT THREAT TO THIS

00:02:39.000 --> 00:02:41.000
COUNTRY.

00:02:41.000 --> 00:02:42.000
Moyers: FOR MONTHS NOW, HIS

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:43.000
ADMINISTRATION HAS BEEN

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:46.000
DETERMINED TO LINK IRAQ TO 9/11.

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:49.000
SEPTEMBER 11 SHOULD SAY TO

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:51.000
THE AMERICAN PEOPLE THAT WE'RE

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:53.000
NOW A BATTLEFIELD.

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:54.000
Moyers: AT LEAST A DOZEN

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:56.000
TIMES DURING THIS PRESS

00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:57.000
CONFERENCE, HE WILL INVOKE 9/11

00:02:57.000 --> 00:02:58.000
AND AL QAEDA TO JUSTIFY A

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:00.000
PREEMPTIVE ATTACK ON A COUNTRY

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:02.000
THAT HAS NOT ATTACKED AMERICA.

00:03:02.000 --> 00:03:04.000
MR. PRESIDENT, IF YOU

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:05.000
DECIDE...

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:06.000
Moyers: BUT THE WHITE HOUSE

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:07.000
PRESS CORPS WILL ASK NO HARD

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:09.000
QUESTIONS TONIGHT ABOUT THOSE

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:10.000
CLAIMS.

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:11.000
LISTEN TO WHAT THE PRESIDENT

00:03:11.000 --> 00:03:13.000
SAYS.

00:03:13.000 --> 00:03:14.000
THIS IS A SCRIPTED...

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:16.000
( LAUGHS )

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:17.000
THANK YOU MR. PRESIDENT...

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:19.000
Moyers: "SCRIPTED."

00:03:19.000 --> 00:03:20.000
SURE ENOUGH, THE PRESIDENT'S

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:22.000
STAFF HAS GIVEN HIM A LIST OF

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:23.000
REPORTERS TO CALL ON.

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:25.000
LET'S SEE HERE.

00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:27.000
ELIZABETH?

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:28.000
GREGORY?

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:31.000
APRIL?

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:32.000
DID YOU HAVE A QUESTION OR DID I

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:33.000
CALL UPON YOU COLD?

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:34.000
NO, I HAVE A QUESTION.

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:35.000
( LAUGHTER )

00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:37.000
OKAY.

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:39.000
I'M SURE YOU DO HAVE A QUESTION.

00:03:39.000 --> 00:03:40.000
HE SORT OF GIGGLED AND

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:42.000
LAUGHED, AND THE REPORTERS SORT

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:43.000
OF LAUGHED.

00:03:43.000 --> 00:03:44.000
AND I DON'T KNOW IF IT WAS OUT

00:03:44.000 --> 00:03:45.000
OF EMBARRASSMENT FOR HIM OR

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:47.000
EMBARRASSMENT FOR THEM, BECAUSE

00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:48.000
THEY STILL CONTINUED TO PLAY

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:49.000
ALONG.

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:50.000
AFTER HIS QUESTION WAS DONE,

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:51.000
THEY ALL SHOT UP THEIR HANDS AND

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:52.000
PRETENDED THEY HAD A CHANCE OF

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:53.000
BEING CALLED ON.

00:03:53.000 --> 00:03:54.000
HOW IS YOUR FAITH GUIDING

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:56.000
YOU?

00:03:56.000 --> 00:03:58.000
MY FAITH SUSTAINS ME BECAUSE

00:03:58.000 --> 00:04:01.000
I PRAY DAILY.

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:03.000
I PRAY FOR GUIDANCE.

00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:04.000
I THINK IT JUST CRYSTALLIZED

00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:06.000
WHAT WAS WRONG WITH THE PRESS

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:07.000
COVERAGE DURING THE RUN-UP TO

00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:08.000
WAR.

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:09.000
I THINK THEY FELT LIKE THE WAR

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:10.000
WAS GOING TO HAPPEN.

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:11.000
AND THEY... THE BEST THING FOR

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:13.000
THEM TO DO WAS TO GET OUT OF THE

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:14.000
WAY.

00:04:14.000 --> 00:04:17.000
THANK YOU FOR YOUR QUESTIONS.

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:26.000
Moyers: OUR STORY BEGINS WITH

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:29.000
THE HORROR OF 9/11.

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:31.000
OH, MY GOD.

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:32.000
OH, MY GOD.

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:33.000
OH, MY GOD.

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:34.000
THAT LOOKS LIKE A SECOND

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:38.000
PLANE.

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:39.000
Moyers: LIKE EVERYONE ELSE,

00:04:39.000 --> 00:04:41.000
JOURNALISTS WERE STUNNED BY THE

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:43.000
DEATH AND DEVASTATION.

00:04:43.000 --> 00:04:44.000
THIS IS AS CLOSE AS WE CAN

00:04:44.000 --> 00:04:45.000
GET TO THE BASE OF THE WORLD

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:46.000
TRADE CENTER.

00:04:46.000 --> 00:04:47.000
YOU CAN SEE THE FIREMEN

00:04:47.000 --> 00:04:48.000
ASSEMBLED HERE.

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:49.000
THE POLICE OFFICERS, F.B.I.

00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:50.000
AGENTS.

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:52.000
AND YOU CAN SEE THE TWO TOWERS,

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:54.000
A HUGE EXPLOSION NOW RAINING

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:55.000
DEBRIS ON ALL OF US.

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:57.000
WE BETTER GET OUT OF THE WAY.

00:04:57.000 --> 00:05:01.000
AND THERE, AS YOU CAN SEE,

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:03.000
PERHAPS THE SECOND TOWER, THE

00:05:03.000 --> 00:05:06.000
FRONT TOWER, THE TOP PORTION OF

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:08.000
WHICH IS COLLAPSING.

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:13.000
GOOD LORD.

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:15.000
IF THERE IS A WAR, IT'S A WAR

00:05:15.000 --> 00:05:16.000
AGAINST TERRORISM THAT

00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:17.000
STARTED... RATHER ONGOING RIGHT

00:05:17.000 --> 00:05:19.000
NOW, IT STARTED HERE AT ABOUT

00:05:19.000 --> 00:05:21.000
QUARTER TO 9:00 THIS MORNING.

00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:23.000
THERE ARE NO WORDS THAT CAN

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:26.000
DESCRIBE THIS.

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:29.000
I WAS DEEPLY MOVED BY 9/11.

00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:30.000
I DON'T KNOW OF ANY AMERICAN WHO

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:31.000
WASN'T.

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:32.000
I THINK WE ALL BOUGHT INTO THAT

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:36.000
THE WORLD HAD CHANGED.

00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:37.000
I THINK THE ATMOSPHERE IN THE

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:40.000
UNITED STATES AFTER SEPTEMBER 11

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:43.000
WAS SO OVERWHELMINGLY PATRIOTIC,

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:46.000
AND OVERWHELMINGLY: "WE MUST DO

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:49.000
SOMETHING ABOUT THIS."

00:05:49.000 --> 00:05:51.000
AND THE PEOPLE WHO KNOCKED

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:53.000
THESE BUILDINGS DOWN WILL HEAR

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:55.000
ALL OF US SOON.

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:59.000
( CHEERS AND APPLAUSE )

00:05:59.000 --> 00:06:02.000
U.S.A.!

00:06:02.000 --> 00:06:04.000
U.S.A.!

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:05.000
U.S.A.!

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:08.000
U.S.A.!

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:10.000
GEORGE BUSH IS THE PRESIDENT.

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:12.000
HE MAKES THE DECISIONS, AND, YOU

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:14.000
KNOW, AS JUST ONE AMERICAN

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:17.000
WHEREVER HE WANTS ME TO LINE UP,

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:19.000
JUST TELL ME WHERE.

00:06:19.000 --> 00:06:20.000
I DIDN'T MEAN IT IN A

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:21.000
JOURNALISTIC SENSE.

00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:22.000
I KNOW IT MAY HAVE COME ACROSS

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:23.000
THAT WAY.

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:24.000
I MEANT IT IN A SENSE AS AN

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:25.000
INDIVIDUAL CITIZEN.

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:27.000
"MR. PRESIDENT, IF YOU NEED ME,

00:06:27.000 --> 00:06:28.000
IF YOU NEED ME TO GO TO HELL AND

00:06:28.000 --> 00:06:29.000
BACK FOR MY COUNTRY, I WILL DO

00:06:29.000 --> 00:06:31.000
IT. "

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:31.000
BUT I'LL TELL YOU THIS, IF THEY

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:33.000
COULD GO DOWN TO GROUND ZERO

00:06:33.000 --> 00:06:35.000
HERE IN LOWER MANHATTAN-- AND

00:06:35.000 --> 00:06:36.000
YOU REFERRED TO IT EARLIER-- AND

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:38.000
SEE THE FOLLOWING, SEE THOSE

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:43.000
FIREMAN...

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:46.000
GO TO BREAK.

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:47.000
OKAY, I'LL TELL YOU WHAT.

00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:48.000
I CAN FINISH IT.

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:49.000
NO, NO.

00:06:49.000 --> 00:06:50.000
DAN, TAKE CARE OF YOURSELF.

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:51.000
WE'LL BE RIGHT BACK HERE WITH

00:06:51.000 --> 00:06:52.000
DAN RATHER.

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:54.000
( APPLAUSE )

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:55.000
Moyers: WHAT I WAS WRESTLING

00:06:55.000 --> 00:06:57.000
WITH THAT NIGHT LISTENING TO YOU

00:06:57.000 --> 00:06:59.000
IS ONCE WE LET OUR EMOTIONS OUT

00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:01.000
AS JOURNALISTS ON THE AIR, ONCE

00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:02.000
WE SAY WE'LL LINE UP WITH THE

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:03.000
PRESIDENT, CAN WE EVER REALLY

00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:05.000
SAY TO THE COUNTRY THE

00:07:05.000 --> 00:07:06.000
PRESIDENT'S OUT OF LINE?

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:08.000
YES, OF COURSE YOU CAN.

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:10.000
OF COURSE YOU CAN.

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:11.000
NO JOURNALIST SHOULD TRY TO BE A

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:14.000
ROBOT AND SAY, "THEY'VE ATTACKED

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:15.000
MY COUNTRY, THEY'VE KILLED

00:07:15.000 --> 00:07:16.000
THOUSANDS OF PEOPLE, BUT I DON'T

00:07:16.000 --> 00:07:19.000
FEEL IT."

00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:20.000
BUT WHAT YOU CAN DO, AND WHAT

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:21.000
SHOULD HAVE BEEN DONE IN THE

00:07:21.000 --> 00:07:23.000
WAKE OF THAT, IS SUCK IT UP AND

00:07:23.000 --> 00:07:24.000
SAY, "OKAY, THAT'S THE WAY I

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:25.000
FEEL.

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:26.000
THAT'S THE WAY I FEEL AS A

00:07:26.000 --> 00:07:27.000
CITIZEN.

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:30.000
BY BEING THE BEST JOURNALIST IT

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:31.000
CAN BE.

00:07:31.000 --> 00:07:33.000
THAT'S THE WAY I CAN BE

00:07:33.000 --> 00:07:35.000
PATRIOTIC."

00:07:35.000 --> 00:07:36.000
BY THE WAY, BILL, THIS IS NOT AN

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:37.000
EXCUSE.

00:07:37.000 --> 00:07:38.000
I DON'T THINK THERE IS ANY

00:07:38.000 --> 00:07:39.000
EXCUSE FOR, YOU KNOW, MY

00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:41.000
PERFORMANCE AND THE PERFORMANCE

00:07:41.000 --> 00:07:43.000
OF THE PRESS, IN GENERAL, IN THE

00:07:43.000 --> 00:07:45.000
ROLL UP TO THE WAR.

00:07:45.000 --> 00:07:46.000
THERE WERE EXCEPTIONS.

00:07:46.000 --> 00:07:47.000
THERE WERE SOME PEOPLE WHO I

00:07:47.000 --> 00:07:49.000
THINK DID A BETTER JOB THAN

00:07:49.000 --> 00:07:50.000
OTHERS.

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:50.000
BUT OVERALL, AND IN THE MAIN,

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:51.000
THERE'S NO QUESTION THAT WE

00:07:51.000 --> 00:07:53.000
DIDN'T DO A GOOD JOB.

00:07:53.000 --> 00:07:55.000
Moyers: AS AMERICANS REACTED

00:07:55.000 --> 00:07:57.000
TO THE ATROCITIES OF A SNEAK

00:07:57.000 --> 00:07:59.000
ATTACK, A POWERFUL SURGE OF

00:07:59.000 --> 00:08:00.000
SOLIDARITY SWEPT ACROSS THE

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:03.000
COUNTRY.

00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:04.000
ONE OF THE THINGS THAT SEEMS

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:05.000
TO BE BINDING ALL AMERICANS

00:08:05.000 --> 00:08:06.000
THESE DAYS, NO MATTER THEIR

00:08:06.000 --> 00:08:08.000
BACKGROUNDS, IN THE AFTERMATH OF

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:11.000
THIS TRAGEDY IS A RENEWED SENSE

00:08:11.000 --> 00:08:13.000
OF PATRIOTISM.

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:15.000
TO SEE SO MANY REPORTERS JUST

00:08:15.000 --> 00:08:16.000
WEARING A LITTLE AMERICAN FLAG

00:08:16.000 --> 00:08:18.000
ON THE LAPELS, TO SEE TIM

00:08:18.000 --> 00:08:19.000
RUSSERT ON "MEET THE PRESS..."

00:08:19.000 --> 00:08:20.000
YEAH.

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:21.000
...WITH THE RED, WHITE AND

00:08:21.000 --> 00:08:22.000
BLUE RIBBONS.

00:08:22.000 --> 00:08:23.000
I THINK IT'S A HUMAN EMOTION

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:24.000
THERE.

00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:26.000
Moyers: AND AS THE

00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:27.000
ADMINISTRATION ORGANIZED TO

00:08:27.000 --> 00:08:28.000
STRIKE BACK AT THE TERRORISTS,

00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:29.000
THERE WAS LITTLE TOLERANCE FOR

00:08:29.000 --> 00:08:30.000
CRITICAL SCRUTINY FROM

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:32.000
JOURNALISTS.

00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:33.000
THERE WAS A PATRIOTIC FERVOR,

00:08:33.000 --> 00:08:35.000
AND THE ADMINISTRATION USED IT.

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:37.000
SO THAT IF YOU CHALLENGED

00:08:37.000 --> 00:08:39.000
ANYTHING, YOU WERE MADE TO FEEL

00:08:39.000 --> 00:08:40.000
THAT THERE WAS SOMETHING WRONG

00:08:40.000 --> 00:08:41.000
WITH THAT.

00:08:41.000 --> 00:08:42.000
Moyers: WALTER ISAACSON WAS

00:08:42.000 --> 00:08:44.000
THEN CHAIRMAN AND CHIEF

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:46.000
EXECUTIVE OFFICER OF CNN.

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:47.000
AND THERE WAS EVEN ALMOST A

00:08:47.000 --> 00:08:49.000
PATRIOTISM POLICE WHICH, YOU

00:08:49.000 --> 00:08:50.000
KNOW, THEY'D BE UP THERE ON THE

00:08:50.000 --> 00:08:51.000
INTERNET SORT OF PICKING

00:08:51.000 --> 00:08:53.000
ANYTHING A CHRISTIANE AMANPOUR

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:54.000
OR SOMEBODY ELSE WOULD SAY AS IF

00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:56.000
IT WERE DISLOYAL.

00:08:56.000 --> 00:08:57.000
Moyers: WE INTERVIEWED A

00:08:57.000 --> 00:08:59.000
FORMER REPORTER AT CNN WHO HAD

00:08:59.000 --> 00:09:00.000
BEEN THERE THROUGH THAT PERIOD.

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:02.000
AND THIS REPORTER SAID THIS

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:03.000
QUOTE: "EVERYBODY ON STAFF JUST

00:09:03.000 --> 00:09:05.000
SORT OF KNEW NOT TO PUSH TOO

00:09:05.000 --> 00:09:06.000
HARD TO DO STORIES CRITICAL OF

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:08.000
THE BUSH ADMINISTRATION."

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:10.000
ESPECIALLY RIGHT AFTER 9/11,

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:11.000
ESPECIALLY WHEN THE WAR IN

00:09:11.000 --> 00:09:13.000
AFGHANISTAN IS GOING ON, THERE

00:09:13.000 --> 00:09:15.000
WAS A REAL SENSE THAT YOU DON'T

00:09:15.000 --> 00:09:17.000
GET THAT CRITICAL OF A

00:09:17.000 --> 00:09:19.000
GOVERNMENT THAT'S LEADING US IN

00:09:19.000 --> 00:09:21.000
WARTIME.

00:09:21.000 --> 00:09:23.000
MOVE OUT!

00:09:23.000 --> 00:09:25.000
Moyers: WHEN AMERICAN FORCES

00:09:25.000 --> 00:09:27.000
WENT AFTER THE TERRORIST BASES

00:09:27.000 --> 00:09:28.000
IN AFGHANISTAN, NETWORK AND

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:30.000
CABLE NEWS REPORTED THE CIVILIAN

00:09:30.000 --> 00:09:32.000
CASUALTIES.

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:33.000
THE PATRIOT POLICE CAME

00:09:33.000 --> 00:09:35.000
KNOCKING.

00:09:35.000 --> 00:09:36.000
WE'D PUT IT ON THE AIR, AND

00:09:36.000 --> 00:09:37.000
BY NATURE OF A 24-HOUR TV

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:39.000
NETWORK, IT WAS REPLAYING OVER

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:40.000
AND OVER AGAIN.

00:09:40.000 --> 00:09:41.000
SO, YOU WOULD GET PHONE CALLS.

00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:42.000
YOU WOULD GET ADVERTISERS.

00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:43.000
YOU WOULD GET THE

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:44.000
ADMINISTRATION.

00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:45.000
Moyers: YOU SAID PRESSURE

00:09:45.000 --> 00:09:46.000
FROM ADVERTISERS?

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:47.000
NOT DIRECT PRESSURE FROM

00:09:47.000 --> 00:09:49.000
ADVERTISERS, BUT BIG PEOPLE IN

00:09:49.000 --> 00:09:51.000
CORPORATIONS WERE CALLING UP AND

00:09:51.000 --> 00:09:52.000
SAYING, "YOU'RE BEING ANTI-

00:09:52.000 --> 00:09:55.000
AMERICAN HERE."

00:09:55.000 --> 00:09:56.000
Moyers: SO ISAACSON SENT HIS

00:09:56.000 --> 00:09:57.000
STAFF A MEMO LEAKED TO THE

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:59.000
"WASHINGTON POST."

00:09:59.000 --> 00:10:00.000
"IT SEEMS PERVERSE," HE SAID,

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:02.000
"TO FOCUS TOO MUCH ON THE

00:10:02.000 --> 00:10:03.000
CASUALTIES OR HARDSHIP IN

00:10:03.000 --> 00:10:05.000
AFGHANISTAN."

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:06.000
THERE'S A BODY UP HERE.

00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:07.000
Moyers: AND HE ORDERED HIS

00:10:07.000 --> 00:10:08.000
REPORTERS AND ANCHORS TO BALANCE

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:10.000
THE IMAGES OF CIVILIAN

00:10:10.000 --> 00:10:12.000
DEVASTATION WITH REMINDERS OF

00:10:12.000 --> 00:10:14.000
SEPTEMBER 11.

00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:15.000
I FELT IF WE PUT INTO

00:10:15.000 --> 00:10:17.000
CONTEXT, WE COULD ALLEVIATE THE

00:10:17.000 --> 00:10:18.000
PRESSURE OF PEOPLE SAYING,

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:19.000
"DON'T EVEN SHOW WHAT'S

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:22.000
HAPPENING IN AFGHANISTAN."

00:10:22.000 --> 00:10:23.000
Moyers: NEWSPAPERS WERE

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:24.000
SQUEEZED, TOO.

00:10:24.000 --> 00:10:25.000
THIS ONE IN FLORIDA TOLD ITS

00:10:25.000 --> 00:10:27.000
EDITORS: "DO NOT USE PHOTOS ON

00:10:27.000 --> 00:10:29.000
PAGE 1A SHOWING CIVILIAN

00:10:29.000 --> 00:10:31.000
CASUALTIES.

00:10:31.000 --> 00:10:33.000
OUR SISTER PAPER HAS DONE SO AND

00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:34.000
RECEIVED HUNDREDS AND HUNDREDS

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:37.000
OF THREATENING E-MAILS."

00:10:37.000 --> 00:10:40.000
AND THEN THERE WAS FOX NEWS,

00:10:40.000 --> 00:10:43.000
WHOSE CHIEF EXECUTIVE, THE

00:10:43.000 --> 00:10:45.000
VETERAN REPUBLICAN OPERATIVE AND

00:10:45.000 --> 00:10:48.000
MEDIA STRATEGIST ROGER AILES,

00:10:48.000 --> 00:10:49.000
HAD PRIVATELY URGED THE WHITE

00:10:49.000 --> 00:10:51.000
HOUSE TO USE THE HARSHEST

00:10:51.000 --> 00:10:54.000
MEASURES POSSIBLE AFTER 9/11.

00:10:54.000 --> 00:10:55.000
SO WE WERE CAUGHT BETWEEN

00:10:55.000 --> 00:10:56.000
THIS PATRIOTIC FERVOR AND A

00:10:56.000 --> 00:10:58.000
COMPETITOR WHO WAS USING THAT TO

00:10:58.000 --> 00:11:00.000
THEIR ADVANTAGE.

00:11:00.000 --> 00:11:01.000
THEY WERE PUSHING THE FACT THAT

00:11:01.000 --> 00:11:03.000
CNN WAS TOO LIBERAL, THAT WE

00:11:03.000 --> 00:11:04.000
WERE SORT OF VAGUELY ANTI-

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:05.000
AMERICAN.

00:11:05.000 --> 00:11:07.000
Moyers: EVEN AS AMERICAN

00:11:07.000 --> 00:11:09.000
TROOPS WERE STILL CHASING OSAMA

00:11:09.000 --> 00:11:11.000
BIN LADEN THROUGH THE MOUNTAINS

00:11:11.000 --> 00:11:13.000
OF AFGHANISTAN, WASHINGTON WAS

00:11:13.000 --> 00:11:15.000
MOVING TOWARD A WIDER WAR.

00:11:15.000 --> 00:11:17.000
WITHIN HOURS AFTER THE ATTACKS

00:11:17.000 --> 00:11:19.000
ON 9/11, DEFENSE SECRETARY

00:11:19.000 --> 00:11:21.000
RUMSFELD PUT SADDAM HUSSEIN ON

00:11:21.000 --> 00:11:22.000
THE HIT LIST.

00:11:22.000 --> 00:11:24.000
AN AIDE TOOK NOTES.

00:11:24.000 --> 00:11:27.000
I KNEW BEFORE 9/11 THAT MANY

00:11:27.000 --> 00:11:28.000
OF THE PEOPLE WHO CAME INTO THE

00:11:28.000 --> 00:11:29.000
ADMINISTRATION WERE COMMITTED TO

00:11:29.000 --> 00:11:32.000
TOPPLING SADDAM HUSSEIN, AND

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:33.000
DOING IT WITH MILITARY FORCE IF

00:11:33.000 --> 00:11:35.000
NECESSARY.

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:36.000
Moyers: DAN RATHER IS TALKING

00:11:36.000 --> 00:11:37.000
ABOUT PROMINENT WASHINGTON

00:11:37.000 --> 00:11:39.000
FIGURES IN AND OUTSIDE OF

00:11:39.000 --> 00:11:40.000
GOVERNMENT KNOWN AS

00:11:40.000 --> 00:11:42.000
NEOCONSERVATIVES.

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:43.000
THEY HAD LONG WANTED TO

00:11:43.000 --> 00:11:44.000
TRANSFORM THE MIDDLE EAST,

00:11:44.000 --> 00:11:45.000
BEGINNING WITH THE REMOVAL OF

00:11:45.000 --> 00:11:47.000
SADDAM HUSSEIN.

00:11:47.000 --> 00:11:48.000
THE TERRORIST ATTACKS GAVE THEM

00:11:48.000 --> 00:11:49.000
THE CHANCE THEY WANTED, AND THE

00:11:49.000 --> 00:11:53.000
MEDIA GAVE THEM A PLATFORM.

00:11:53.000 --> 00:11:54.000
RICHARD PERLE, NEXT PHASE:

00:11:54.000 --> 00:11:55.000
SADDAM HUSSEIN?

00:11:55.000 --> 00:11:56.000
ABSOLUTELY.

00:11:56.000 --> 00:11:57.000
ONE PERSON CLOSE TO THE

00:11:57.000 --> 00:11:59.000
DEBATE SAID TO ME THIS WEEK THAT

00:11:59.000 --> 00:12:00.000
IT'S NO LONGER A QUESTION OF

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:01.000
"IF," IT'S A QUESTION OF "HOW"

00:12:01.000 --> 00:12:04.000
WE GO AFTER SADDAM HUSSEIN.

00:12:04.000 --> 00:12:05.000
Moyers: IN THE WEEKS AFTER

00:12:05.000 --> 00:12:06.000
9/11, THEY SEEMED TO BE ON EVERY

00:12:06.000 --> 00:12:09.000
CHANNEL, GUNNING FOR HUSSEIN.

00:12:09.000 --> 00:12:10.000
YOU ARE PROBABLY THE HAWKIEST

00:12:10.000 --> 00:12:11.000
OF THE HAWKS ON THIS.

00:12:11.000 --> 00:12:13.000
WHY?

00:12:13.000 --> 00:12:14.000
WELL, I DON'T KNOW THAT I

00:12:14.000 --> 00:12:15.000
ACCEPT THAT CHARACTERIZATION,

00:12:15.000 --> 00:12:17.000
BUT IT'S PROBABLY NOT TOO FAR

00:12:17.000 --> 00:12:18.000
OFF.

00:12:18.000 --> 00:12:21.000
I THINK THAT THE BAGHDAD REGIME

00:12:21.000 --> 00:12:24.000
IS A SERIOUS DANGER TO WORLD

00:12:24.000 --> 00:12:25.000
PEACE.

00:12:25.000 --> 00:12:27.000
WEAPONS OF MASS DESTRUCTION

00:12:27.000 --> 00:12:28.000
IN THE HANDS OF SADDAM HUSSEIN,

00:12:28.000 --> 00:12:30.000
PLUS HIS KNOWN CONTACT WITH

00:12:30.000 --> 00:12:31.000
TERRORISTS, INCLUDING AL QAEDA

00:12:31.000 --> 00:12:33.000
TERRORISTS, IS SIMPLY A THREAT

00:12:33.000 --> 00:12:34.000
TOO LARGE TO CONTINUE TO

00:12:34.000 --> 00:12:36.000
TOLERATE.

00:12:36.000 --> 00:12:37.000
Moyers: AMONG THEIR LEADING

00:12:37.000 --> 00:12:38.000
SPOKESMEN WERE RICHARD PERLE AND

00:12:38.000 --> 00:12:40.000
JAMES WOOLSEY.

00:12:40.000 --> 00:12:41.000
BOTH SAT ON THE DEFENSE POLICY

00:12:41.000 --> 00:12:43.000
BOARD ADVISING DONALD RUMSFELD.

00:12:43.000 --> 00:12:45.000
AND THEY USED THEIR INSIDE

00:12:45.000 --> 00:12:47.000
STATUS TO ASSURE THE PRESS THAT

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:48.000
OVERTHROWING HUSSEIN WOULD BE

00:12:48.000 --> 00:12:50.000
EASY.

00:12:50.000 --> 00:12:51.000
WE WOULD BE SEEN AS

00:12:51.000 --> 00:12:53.000
LIBERATORS IN IRAQ.

00:12:53.000 --> 00:12:54.000
Moyers: MAJOR NEWSPAPERS AND

00:12:54.000 --> 00:12:55.000
MAGAZINES GAVE THEM PRIME SPACE

00:12:55.000 --> 00:12:58.000
TO MAKE THEIR CASE, INCLUDING

00:12:58.000 --> 00:12:59.000
THE POSSIBILITY THAT 9/11 HAD

00:12:59.000 --> 00:13:02.000
BEEN "SPONSORED, SUPPORTED AND

00:13:02.000 --> 00:13:03.000
PERHAPS EVEN ORDERED BY SADDAM

00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:05.000
HUSSEIN."

00:13:05.000 --> 00:13:06.000
THE PRESIDENT, THEY SAID, SHOULD

00:13:06.000 --> 00:13:08.000
TAKE PREEMPTIVE ACTION.

00:13:08.000 --> 00:13:09.000
THE BIGGEST MISTAKE WE HAVE

00:13:09.000 --> 00:13:11.000
MADE-- IT'S OUR MISTAKE, IT'S

00:13:11.000 --> 00:13:12.000
NOT THE MISTAKE OF THE ARABS--

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:13.000
WAS NOT FINISHING OFF SADDAM

00:13:13.000 --> 00:13:16.000
HUSSEIN IN 1991.

00:13:16.000 --> 00:13:17.000
Moyers: NO ONE GOT MORE AIR

00:13:17.000 --> 00:13:19.000
TIME FROM AN ARMCHAIR THAN BILL

00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:20.000
KRISTOL, EDITOR OF THE "WEEKLY

00:13:20.000 --> 00:13:22.000
STANDARD" AND A MEDIA-SAVVY

00:13:22.000 --> 00:13:24.000
REPUBLICAN STRATEGIST.

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:26.000
IN THE 1990s, KRISTOL ORGANIZED

00:13:26.000 --> 00:13:28.000
A CAMPAIGN FOR INCREASED

00:13:28.000 --> 00:13:30.000
MILITARY SPENDING AND A MUSCULAR

00:13:30.000 --> 00:13:32.000
FOREIGN POLICY.

00:13:32.000 --> 00:13:34.000
IN 1998, HE AND HIS ALLIES WROTE

00:13:34.000 --> 00:13:36.000
PRESIDENT BILL CLINTON URGING

00:13:36.000 --> 00:13:37.000
HIM TO REMOVE SADDAM HUSSEIN

00:13:37.000 --> 00:13:39.000
FROM POWER.

00:13:39.000 --> 00:13:41.000
AND NOW, JUST DAYS AFTER 9/11,

00:13:41.000 --> 00:13:43.000
WITH MANY OF THEIR ALLIES

00:13:43.000 --> 00:13:45.000
SERVING IN THE ADMINISTRATION,

00:13:45.000 --> 00:13:46.000
THEY WROTE AN OPEN LETTER TO

00:13:46.000 --> 00:13:48.000
PRESIDENT BUSH, CALLING FOR

00:13:48.000 --> 00:13:50.000
REGIME CHANGE IN BAGHDAD.

00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:52.000
OVER THE COMING MONTHS,

00:13:52.000 --> 00:13:53.000
KRISTOL'S "WEEKLY STANDARD" KEPT

00:13:53.000 --> 00:13:55.000
UP THE DRUMBEAT.

00:13:55.000 --> 00:13:56.000
WHAT ARE THE CONSEQUENCES IF

00:13:56.000 --> 00:13:58.000
THE U.S. DOES NOT FINISH OFF

00:13:58.000 --> 00:14:01.000
THIS SADDAM HUSSEIN AS A SECOND

00:14:01.000 --> 00:14:03.000
STEP IN THE WAR ON TERRORISM?

00:14:03.000 --> 00:14:05.000
IT WOULD MEAN THAT THE

00:14:05.000 --> 00:14:06.000
PRESIDENT, HAVING DECLARED A

00:14:06.000 --> 00:14:08.000
GLOBAL WAR ON TERRORISM, DIDN'T

00:14:08.000 --> 00:14:09.000
FOLLOW THROUGH, DIDN'T TAKE OUT

00:14:09.000 --> 00:14:10.000
THE MOST THREATENING TERRORIST

00:14:10.000 --> 00:14:13.000
STATE IN THE WORLD.

00:14:13.000 --> 00:14:15.000
Moyers: THE EDITORIAL PAGE OF

00:14:15.000 --> 00:14:16.000
THE "WALL STREET JOURNAL" SIGNED

00:14:16.000 --> 00:14:19.000
ON, AND SO DID HIGH-PROFILE

00:14:19.000 --> 00:14:20.000
PUNDITS LIKE THE "NEW YORK

00:14:20.000 --> 00:14:22.000
TIMES'" WILLIAM SAFIRE.

00:14:22.000 --> 00:14:24.000
SAFIRE, WILL YOU WAGER MS.

00:14:24.000 --> 00:14:25.000
WRIGHT RIGHT NOW THAT SADDAM

00:14:25.000 --> 00:14:26.000
WILL BE OUT OF POWER BY THE END

00:14:26.000 --> 00:14:27.000
OF 2002?

00:14:27.000 --> 00:14:28.000
ABSOLUTELY.

00:14:28.000 --> 00:14:29.000
I'LL SEE YOU HERE A YEAR FROM

00:14:29.000 --> 00:14:31.000
NOW.

00:14:31.000 --> 00:14:32.000
IF YOU GO AFTER IRAQ YOU'RE

00:14:32.000 --> 00:14:33.000
GOING TO LOSE A LOT OF ALLIES,

00:14:33.000 --> 00:14:34.000
BUT WHO CARES?

00:14:34.000 --> 00:14:36.000
Moyers: CHARLES KRAUTHAMMER

00:14:36.000 --> 00:14:37.000
AND OTHER TOP COLUMNISTS AT THE

00:14:37.000 --> 00:14:39.000
"WASHINGTON POST" ALSO SAW THE

00:14:39.000 --> 00:14:40.000
HAND OF SADDAM HUSSEIN IN THE

00:14:40.000 --> 00:14:42.000
TERRORIST ATTACKS.

00:14:42.000 --> 00:14:44.000
JIM HOAGLAND IMPLICATED HUSSEIN

00:14:44.000 --> 00:14:45.000
WITHIN HOURS AFTER THE SUICIDE

00:14:45.000 --> 00:14:48.000
BOMBERS STRUCK ON 9/11.

00:14:48.000 --> 00:14:50.000
AND THE "POST'S" GEORGE WILL

00:14:50.000 --> 00:14:52.000
FIRED AWAY ON THE TALK SHOWS.

00:14:52.000 --> 00:14:55.000
THE ADMINISTRATION KNOWS HE'S

00:14:55.000 --> 00:14:56.000
VOWED... HUSSEIN HAS VOWED

00:14:56.000 --> 00:14:58.000
REVENGE, HE HAS ANTHRAX, HE

00:14:58.000 --> 00:14:59.000
LOVES BIOLOGICAL WEAPONS, HE HAS

00:14:59.000 --> 00:15:01.000
TERRORIST TRAINING CAMPS,

00:15:01.000 --> 00:15:03.000
INCLUDING A 707 TO PRACTICE ON.

00:15:03.000 --> 00:15:05.000
Moyers: IT WAS PROVING

00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:06.000
DIFFICULT TO DISTINGUISH THE

00:15:06.000 --> 00:15:08.000
OPINION OF THE PUNDITS FROM THE

00:15:08.000 --> 00:15:10.000
POLICIES OF THE ADMINISTRATION.

00:15:10.000 --> 00:15:11.000
BUT AS THE HULLABALOO OVER

00:15:11.000 --> 00:15:13.000
SADDAM GREW IN WASHINGTON, BOB

00:15:13.000 --> 00:15:15.000
SIMON OF CBS NEWS' "60 MINUTES"

00:15:15.000 --> 00:15:17.000
WAS DUMBFOUNDED.

00:15:17.000 --> 00:15:19.000
HE'S BASED IN THE MIDDLE EAST.

00:15:19.000 --> 00:15:20.000
FROM OVERSEAS WE HAD A

00:15:20.000 --> 00:15:22.000
CLEARER VIEW.

00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:23.000
I MEAN, WE KNEW THINGS OR

00:15:23.000 --> 00:15:25.000
SUSPECTED THINGS THAT PERHAPS

00:15:25.000 --> 00:15:27.000
THE WASHINGTON PRESS CORPS COULD

00:15:27.000 --> 00:15:28.000
NOT SUSPECT.

00:15:28.000 --> 00:15:29.000
FOR EXAMPLE, THE ABSURDITY OF

00:15:29.000 --> 00:15:31.000
PUTTING UP A CONNECTION BETWEEN

00:15:31.000 --> 00:15:33.000
SADDAM HUSSEIN AND AL QAEDA.

00:15:33.000 --> 00:15:36.000
Moyers: ABSURDITY.

00:15:36.000 --> 00:15:37.000
THE WASHINGTON PRESS CORPS

00:15:37.000 --> 00:15:40.000
CANNOT QUESTION AN ABSURDITY?

00:15:40.000 --> 00:15:41.000
WELL, MAYBE THE WASHINGTON

00:15:41.000 --> 00:15:44.000
PRESS CORPS, BASED INSIDE THE

00:15:44.000 --> 00:15:46.000
BELT, WASN'T AS AWARE AS THOSE

00:15:46.000 --> 00:15:49.000
OF US WHO ARE BASED IN THE

00:15:49.000 --> 00:15:50.000
MIDDLE EAST AND WHO SPEND A LOT

00:15:50.000 --> 00:15:51.000
OF TIME IN IRAQ.

00:15:51.000 --> 00:15:53.000
I MEAN, WHEN THE WASHINGTON

00:15:53.000 --> 00:15:54.000
PRESS CORPS TRAVELS, IT TRAVELS

00:15:54.000 --> 00:15:55.000
WITH THE PRESIDENT OR WITH THE

00:15:55.000 --> 00:15:57.000
SECRETARY OF STATE AND...

00:15:57.000 --> 00:15:59.000
Moyers: IN A BUBBLE.

00:15:59.000 --> 00:16:00.000
YEAH, IN A BUBBLE.

00:16:00.000 --> 00:16:01.000
WHEREAS WE WHO'VE SPENT WEEKS

00:16:01.000 --> 00:16:02.000
JUST WALKING THE STREETS OF

00:16:02.000 --> 00:16:04.000
BAGHDAD, AND IN OTHER SITUATIONS

00:16:04.000 --> 00:16:07.000
IN BAGHDAD, JUST WERE SCRATCHING

00:16:07.000 --> 00:16:09.000
OUR HEADS IN WAYS THAT PERHAPS

00:16:09.000 --> 00:16:10.000
THAT THE WASHINGTON PRESS CORPS

00:16:10.000 --> 00:16:12.000
COULD NOT.

00:16:12.000 --> 00:16:13.000
Moyers: SIMON WAS UNDER NO

00:16:13.000 --> 00:16:14.000
ILLUSIONS ABOUT SADDAM HUSSEIN.

00:16:14.000 --> 00:16:16.000
DURING THE FIRST GULF WAR, HE

00:16:16.000 --> 00:16:17.000
AND HIS CAMERA CREW WERE

00:16:17.000 --> 00:16:19.000
ARRESTED BY IRAQI FORCES AND

00:16:19.000 --> 00:16:21.000
BRUTALIZED FOR 40 DAYS BEFORE

00:16:21.000 --> 00:16:23.000
BEING RELEASED.

00:16:23.000 --> 00:16:24.000
WE'RE GOING HOME, WHICH IS

00:16:24.000 --> 00:16:27.000
THE PLACE YOU GO TO AFTER A WAR

00:16:27.000 --> 00:16:28.000
WHEN... IF YOU'VE BEEN AS LUCKY

00:16:28.000 --> 00:16:30.000
AS WE'VE BEEN.

00:16:30.000 --> 00:16:31.000
Moyers: IT DIDN'T MAKE SENSE

00:16:31.000 --> 00:16:33.000
TO SIMON THAT THE DICTATOR WOULD

00:16:33.000 --> 00:16:35.000
TRUST ISLAMIC TERRORISTS.

00:16:35.000 --> 00:16:38.000
SADDAM, AS MOST TYRANTS, WAS

00:16:38.000 --> 00:16:40.000
A TOTAL CONTROL FREAK.

00:16:40.000 --> 00:16:43.000
HE WANTED TOTAL CONTROL OF HIS

00:16:43.000 --> 00:16:45.000
REGIME, TOTAL CONTROL OF THE

00:16:45.000 --> 00:16:47.000
COUNTRY.

00:16:47.000 --> 00:16:49.000
AND TO INTRODUCE A WILD CARD

00:16:49.000 --> 00:16:51.000
LIKE AL QAEDA IN ANY SENSE WAS

00:16:51.000 --> 00:16:54.000
JUST SOMETHING HE WOULD NOT DO.

00:16:54.000 --> 00:16:55.000
SO I JUST DIDN'T BELIEVE IT FOR

00:16:55.000 --> 00:16:57.000
AN INSTANT.

00:16:57.000 --> 00:16:58.000
AND SOME OF THE THINGS THAT

00:16:58.000 --> 00:16:59.000
WERE SAID, MANY OF THE THINGS

00:16:59.000 --> 00:17:01.000
THAT WERE SAID ABOUT IRAQ,

00:17:01.000 --> 00:17:03.000
DIDN'T MAKE SENSE.

00:17:03.000 --> 00:17:05.000
AND THAT REALLY PROMPTS YOU TO

00:17:05.000 --> 00:17:07.000
ASK, "WAIT A MINUTE, IS THIS

00:17:07.000 --> 00:17:10.000
TRUE?

00:17:10.000 --> 00:17:11.000
DOES EVERYONE AGREE THAT THIS IS

00:17:11.000 --> 00:17:13.000
TRUE?

00:17:13.000 --> 00:17:14.000
DOES ANYONE THINK THIS IS NOT

00:17:14.000 --> 00:17:16.000
TRUE?"

00:17:16.000 --> 00:17:17.000
THIS IS WHAT WE'RE GOING TO DO,

00:17:17.000 --> 00:17:19.000
THIS IS PLAN-A NOW.

00:17:19.000 --> 00:17:20.000
Moyers: JOHN WALCOTT WASN'T

00:17:20.000 --> 00:17:21.000
BUYING THE OFFICIAL LINE,

00:17:21.000 --> 00:17:22.000
EITHER.

00:17:22.000 --> 00:17:23.000
THE BUREAU CHIEF OF KNIGHT

00:17:23.000 --> 00:17:24.000
RIDDER NEWS SERVICE, HE AND HIS

00:17:24.000 --> 00:17:25.000
REPORTERS COVERED WASHINGTON FOR

00:17:25.000 --> 00:17:27.000
32 NEWSPAPERS SPREAD ACROSS THE

00:17:27.000 --> 00:17:29.000
COUNTRY.

00:17:29.000 --> 00:17:31.000
OUR READERS AREN'T HERE IN

00:17:31.000 --> 00:17:32.000
WASHINGTON.

00:17:32.000 --> 00:17:33.000
THEY AREN'T UP IN NEW YORK.

00:17:33.000 --> 00:17:34.000
THEY AREN'T THE PEOPLE WHO SEND

00:17:34.000 --> 00:17:36.000
OTHER PEOPLE'S KIDS TO WAR.

00:17:36.000 --> 00:17:37.000
THEY'RE THE PEOPLE WHO GET SENT

00:17:37.000 --> 00:17:39.000
TO WAR.

00:17:39.000 --> 00:17:40.000
AND WE FELT AN OBLIGATION TO

00:17:40.000 --> 00:17:41.000
THEM TO EXPLAIN WHY THAT MIGHT

00:17:41.000 --> 00:17:44.000
HAPPEN.

00:17:44.000 --> 00:17:47.000
WE WERE DETERMINED TO SCRUTINIZE

00:17:47.000 --> 00:17:49.000
THE ADMINISTRATION'S CASE FOR

00:17:49.000 --> 00:17:50.000
WAR AS CLOSELY AS WE POSSIBLY

00:17:50.000 --> 00:17:52.000
COULD, AND THAT'S WHAT WE SET

00:17:52.000 --> 00:17:54.000
OUT TO DO.

00:17:54.000 --> 00:17:55.000
Moyers: SO AS HE LISTENED TO

00:17:55.000 --> 00:17:57.000
PUNDITS AND OFFICIALS TALKING

00:17:57.000 --> 00:17:58.000
ABOUT SADDAM HUSSEIN'S SUPPOSED

00:17:58.000 --> 00:18:00.000
CONNECTIONS TO 9/11, WALCOTT WAS

00:18:00.000 --> 00:18:02.000
SKEPTICAL.

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:03.000
IT WAS NOT CLEAR TO US WHY

00:18:03.000 --> 00:18:05.000
ANYONE WAS ASKING QUESTIONS

00:18:05.000 --> 00:18:07.000
ABOUT IRAQ IN THE WAKE OF AN

00:18:07.000 --> 00:18:09.000
ATTACK THAT HAD AL QAEDA WRITTEN

00:18:09.000 --> 00:18:10.000
ALL OVER IT.

00:18:10.000 --> 00:18:12.000
Moyers: HE ASSIGNED HIS TWO

00:18:12.000 --> 00:18:13.000
TOP REPORTERS TO INVESTIGATE THE

00:18:13.000 --> 00:18:15.000
CLAIMS.

00:18:15.000 --> 00:18:16.000
BETWEEN THEM, WARREN STROBEL AND

00:18:16.000 --> 00:18:18.000
JONATHAN LANDAY HAD MORE THAN 40

00:18:18.000 --> 00:18:20.000
YEARS EXPERIENCE REPORTING ON

00:18:20.000 --> 00:18:22.000
FOREIGN AFFAIRS AND NATIONAL

00:18:22.000 --> 00:18:24.000
SECURITY.

00:18:24.000 --> 00:18:25.000
THEY HAD LOTS OF SOURCES TO CALL

00:18:25.000 --> 00:18:26.000
ON.

00:18:26.000 --> 00:18:27.000
WE WERE BASICALLY, I THINK,

00:18:27.000 --> 00:18:28.000
HEARING TWO DIFFERENT MESSAGES

00:18:28.000 --> 00:18:30.000
FROM... THERE'S A MESSAGE, THE

00:18:30.000 --> 00:18:31.000
PUBLIC MESSAGE THE

00:18:31.000 --> 00:18:32.000
ADMINISTRATION WAS GIVING OUT

00:18:32.000 --> 00:18:33.000
ABOUT IRAQ.

00:18:33.000 --> 00:18:34.000
IT'S W.M.D., THE FACT THERE WAS

00:18:34.000 --> 00:18:35.000
AN IMMEDIATE THREAT, GRAVE

00:18:35.000 --> 00:18:37.000
THREAT, GATHERING THREAT.

00:18:37.000 --> 00:18:38.000
BUT THAT WAS SO DIFFERENT FROM

00:18:38.000 --> 00:18:40.000
WHAT WE WERE HEARING FROM PEOPLE

00:18:40.000 --> 00:18:41.000
ON THE INSIDE, PEOPLE WE HAD

00:18:41.000 --> 00:18:43.000
KNOWN IN MANY CASES FOR YEARS

00:18:43.000 --> 00:18:45.000
AND TRUSTED.

00:18:45.000 --> 00:18:46.000
Moyers: THEY WENT ABOUT THEIR

00:18:46.000 --> 00:18:47.000
REPORTING THE OLD-FASHIONED WAY

00:18:47.000 --> 00:18:49.000
WITH SHOE LEATHER, TRACKING DOWN

00:18:49.000 --> 00:18:51.000
AND MEETING WITH SOURCES DEEP

00:18:51.000 --> 00:18:52.000
INSIDE THE INTELLIGENCE

00:18:52.000 --> 00:18:53.000
COMMUNITY.

00:18:53.000 --> 00:18:54.000
WHEN YOU'RE TALKING TO THE

00:18:54.000 --> 00:18:55.000
WORKING GRUNTS, YOU KNOW,

00:18:55.000 --> 00:18:57.000
UNIFORM MILITARY OFFICERS,

00:18:57.000 --> 00:18:58.000
INTELLIGENCE PROFESSIONALS,

00:18:58.000 --> 00:19:00.000
PROFESSIONAL DIPLOMATS, THOSE

00:19:00.000 --> 00:19:01.000
PEOPLE ARE MORE LIKELY THAN

00:19:01.000 --> 00:19:04.000
NOT-- NOT ALWAYS, OF COURSE, BUT

00:19:04.000 --> 00:19:05.000
MORE LIKELY THAN NOT-- TO TELL

00:19:05.000 --> 00:19:06.000
YOU SOME VERSION OF THE TRUTH,

00:19:06.000 --> 00:19:07.000
AND TO BE KNOWLEDGEABLE ABOUT

00:19:07.000 --> 00:19:08.000
WHAT THEY'RE TALKING ABOUT WHEN

00:19:08.000 --> 00:19:10.000
IT COMES TO TERRORISM OR THE

00:19:10.000 --> 00:19:12.000
MIDDLE EAST, THINGS LIKE THAT.

00:19:12.000 --> 00:19:14.000
Moyers: STROBEL LEARNED THAT

00:19:14.000 --> 00:19:15.000
WITHIN TWO WEEKS AFTER 9/11,

00:19:15.000 --> 00:19:17.000
SENIOR INTELLIGENCE OFFICERS

00:19:17.000 --> 00:19:19.000
WERE GROWING CONCERNED THAT THE

00:19:19.000 --> 00:19:20.000
BUSH ADMINISTRATION WAS

00:19:20.000 --> 00:19:21.000
STRETCHING LITTLE BITS AND

00:19:21.000 --> 00:19:23.000
PIECES OF INFORMATION TO CONNECT

00:19:23.000 --> 00:19:25.000
SADDAM HUSSEIN TO AL QAEDA WITH

00:19:25.000 --> 00:19:29.000
NO HARD EVIDENCE.

00:19:29.000 --> 00:19:31.000
THERE WAS A LOT OF SKEPTICISM

00:19:31.000 --> 00:19:33.000
AMONG OUR EDITORS BECAUSE WHAT

00:19:33.000 --> 00:19:35.000
WE WERE WRITING WAS SO AT ODDS

00:19:35.000 --> 00:19:36.000
WITH WHAT MOST OF THE REST OF

00:19:36.000 --> 00:19:38.000
THE WASHINGTON PRESS CORPS WAS

00:19:38.000 --> 00:19:40.000
REPORTING AND SOME OF OUR PAPERS

00:19:40.000 --> 00:19:41.000
FRANKLY, JUST DIDN'T RUN THE

00:19:41.000 --> 00:19:42.000
STORIES.

00:19:42.000 --> 00:19:43.000
THEY HAD ACCESS TO THE "NEW YORK

00:19:43.000 --> 00:19:44.000
TIMES" WIRE AND THE "WASHINGTON

00:19:44.000 --> 00:19:46.000
POST" WIRE, AND THEY CHOSE THOSE

00:19:46.000 --> 00:19:49.000
STORIES INSTEAD.

00:19:49.000 --> 00:19:51.000
Moyers: WITHIN THE MONTH,

00:19:51.000 --> 00:19:52.000
STROBEL FOUND OUT THE PENTAGON

00:19:52.000 --> 00:19:53.000
HAD ALREADY DISPATCHED JAMES

00:19:53.000 --> 00:19:55.000
WOOLSEY TO EUROPE LOOKING FOR

00:19:55.000 --> 00:19:56.000
ANY SHRED OF EVIDENCE TO

00:19:56.000 --> 00:19:59.000
INCRIMINATE HUSSEIN.

00:19:59.000 --> 00:20:00.000
HE DID THIS EVEN KNOWING THAT

00:20:00.000 --> 00:20:03.000
THE C.I.A. HAD ALREADY ANALYZED

00:20:03.000 --> 00:20:05.000
THIS CAREFULLY AND FOUND NO SUCH

00:20:05.000 --> 00:20:06.000
LINKS.

00:20:06.000 --> 00:20:07.000
SO THE MORE I THOUGHT ABOUT

00:20:07.000 --> 00:20:08.000
THAT, THE MORE IT JUST DIDN'T

00:20:08.000 --> 00:20:11.000
SEEM TO MAKE SENSE.

00:20:11.000 --> 00:20:12.000
Moyers: KNIGHT RIDDER'S EARLY

00:20:12.000 --> 00:20:13.000
SKEPTICISM WAS A RARITY INSIDE

00:20:13.000 --> 00:20:16.000
THE BELTWAY BUBBLE.

00:20:16.000 --> 00:20:17.000
A DECISION TO GO TO WAR, EVEN

00:20:17.000 --> 00:20:18.000
AGAINST AN EIGHTH-RATE POWER

00:20:18.000 --> 00:20:21.000
SUCH AS IRAQ, IS THE MOST

00:20:21.000 --> 00:20:24.000
SERIOUS DECISION THAT A

00:20:24.000 --> 00:20:26.000
GOVERNMENT CAN EVER MAKE AND IT

00:20:26.000 --> 00:20:27.000
DESERVES THE MOST SERIOUS KIND

00:20:27.000 --> 00:20:30.000
OF SCRUTINY THAT WE IN THE MEDIA

00:20:30.000 --> 00:20:32.000
CAN GIVE IT.

00:20:32.000 --> 00:20:34.000
IS THIS REALLY NECESSARY?

00:20:34.000 --> 00:20:36.000
IS IT NECESSARY TO SEND OUR

00:20:36.000 --> 00:20:38.000
YOUNG MEN AND WOMEN TO GO KILL

00:20:38.000 --> 00:20:39.000
SOMEBODY ELSE'S YOUNG MEN AND

00:20:39.000 --> 00:20:41.000
WOMEN?

00:20:41.000 --> 00:20:42.000
Moyers: THAT MEANT ASKING

00:20:42.000 --> 00:20:43.000
QUESTIONS ABOUT THE SOURCES OF

00:20:43.000 --> 00:20:44.000
INFORMATION THE PRESS AND

00:20:44.000 --> 00:20:46.000
GOVERNMENT WERE RELYING ON,

00:20:46.000 --> 00:20:49.000
INCLUDING, NOTABLY, THIS MAN,

00:20:49.000 --> 00:20:51.000
AHMED CHALABI.

00:20:51.000 --> 00:20:52.000
AFTER THE FIRST GULF WAR,

00:20:52.000 --> 00:20:54.000
AMERICANS HAD INSTALLED CHALABI

00:20:54.000 --> 00:20:56.000
AS THE LEADER OF IRAQI EXILES

00:20:56.000 --> 00:20:57.000
SEEKING REGIME CHANGE IN

00:20:57.000 --> 00:20:59.000
BAGHDAD.

00:20:59.000 --> 00:21:01.000
NOW HE WAS ALL OVER WASHINGTON

00:21:01.000 --> 00:21:02.000
AS THE ADMINISTRATION'S AND THE

00:21:02.000 --> 00:21:04.000
NEO-CONSERVATIVES' STAR WITNESS

00:21:04.000 --> 00:21:05.000
AGAINST SADDAM.

00:21:05.000 --> 00:21:06.000
HELLO.

00:21:06.000 --> 00:21:07.000
CHALABI'S MOTIVES WERE ALWAYS

00:21:07.000 --> 00:21:09.000
PERFECTLY CLEAR IN THIS AND

00:21:09.000 --> 00:21:10.000
UNDERSTANDABLE.

00:21:10.000 --> 00:21:12.000
HE WAS AN IRAQI.

00:21:12.000 --> 00:21:13.000
HE DIDN'T WANT HIS COUNTRY RUN

00:21:13.000 --> 00:21:14.000
BY A THUG AND A MURDERER, A MASS

00:21:14.000 --> 00:21:17.000
MURDERER AND A CROOK, AND

00:21:17.000 --> 00:21:21.000
EVERYTHING HE SAID HAD TO BE

00:21:21.000 --> 00:21:22.000
LOOKED AT IN THAT LIGHT AND

00:21:22.000 --> 00:21:23.000
SCRUTINIZED IN THAT LIGHT.

00:21:23.000 --> 00:21:27.000
AND WHY ANYONE WOULD GIVE HIM A

00:21:27.000 --> 00:21:29.000
FREE PASS, OR ANYONE ELSE A FREE

00:21:29.000 --> 00:21:31.000
PASS FOR THAT MATTER, ON A

00:21:31.000 --> 00:21:32.000
MATTER AS IMPORTANT AS GOING TO

00:21:32.000 --> 00:21:35.000
WAR, IS BEYOND ME.

00:21:35.000 --> 00:21:36.000
CHALABI WAS A CREATURE OF

00:21:36.000 --> 00:21:38.000
AMERICAN PROPAGANDA TO A LARGE

00:21:38.000 --> 00:21:39.000
DEGREE.

00:21:39.000 --> 00:21:42.000
IT WAS AN AMERICAN COMPANY, THE

00:21:42.000 --> 00:21:44.000
RENDON GROUP, THAT, WORKING

00:21:44.000 --> 00:21:46.000
SECRETLY WITH THE C.I.A.,

00:21:46.000 --> 00:21:48.000
BASICALLY CREATED HIS

00:21:48.000 --> 00:21:49.000
ORGANIZATION, THE IRAQI NATIONAL

00:21:49.000 --> 00:21:52.000
CONGRESS, AND PUT CHALABI IN

00:21:52.000 --> 00:21:55.000
CHARGE, BASICALLY.

00:21:55.000 --> 00:21:57.000
Moyers: JAMES BAMFORD IS AN

00:21:57.000 --> 00:21:58.000
INDEPENDENT JOURNALIST WHOSE

00:21:58.000 --> 00:22:00.000
SPECIALTY IS THE INTELLIGENCE

00:22:00.000 --> 00:22:01.000
WORLD.

00:22:01.000 --> 00:22:03.000
FROM THE VERY BEGINNING,

00:22:03.000 --> 00:22:04.000
CHALABI WAS PAID A LOT OF MONEY

00:22:04.000 --> 00:22:06.000
FROM THE U.S. TAXPAYERS.

00:22:06.000 --> 00:22:08.000
THE C.I.A. PAID HIM ORIGINALLY

00:22:08.000 --> 00:22:10.000
ABOUT $350,000 A MONTH TO

00:22:10.000 --> 00:22:12.000
CHALABI AND HIS ORGANIZATION.

00:22:12.000 --> 00:22:14.000
THE C.I.A. FINALLY CAUGHT ON IN

00:22:14.000 --> 00:22:17.000
THE MID-'90s THAT CHALABI WAS A

00:22:17.000 --> 00:22:18.000
CON MAN, BASICALLY, AND THEY

00:22:18.000 --> 00:22:20.000
DROPPED HIM.

00:22:20.000 --> 00:22:21.000
Moyers: CHALABI'S HANDLERS IN

00:22:21.000 --> 00:22:22.000
WASHINGTON WERE NOT DETERRED BY

00:22:22.000 --> 00:22:24.000
THAT STAIN ON HIS CREDIBILITY.

00:22:24.000 --> 00:22:26.000
HE CHARMED CONGRESS OUT OF

00:22:26.000 --> 00:22:27.000
MILLIONS MORE DOLLARS FOR HIS

00:22:27.000 --> 00:22:28.000
CAUSE, AND HAD THE PRESS EATING

00:22:28.000 --> 00:22:30.000
OUT OF HIS HAND.

00:22:30.000 --> 00:22:31.000
HE MADE A LOT OF FRIENDS IN

00:22:31.000 --> 00:22:32.000
THE MEDIA.

00:22:32.000 --> 00:22:33.000
AND HE CONVINCED A LOT OF PEOPLE

00:22:33.000 --> 00:22:34.000
THAT HE WAS LEGITIMATE EVEN

00:22:34.000 --> 00:22:35.000
THOUGH THE C.I.A. HAD DROPPED

00:22:35.000 --> 00:22:37.000
HIM.

00:22:37.000 --> 00:22:39.000
Moyers: WHEN CHALABI MADE

00:22:39.000 --> 00:22:40.000
SELECTED IRAQI DEFECTORS

00:22:40.000 --> 00:22:42.000
AVAILABLE TO THE PRESS IT WAS A

00:22:42.000 --> 00:22:44.000
WIN/WIN GAME: THE DEFECTORS GOT

00:22:44.000 --> 00:22:45.000
A PLATFORM; JOURNALISTS GOT BIG

00:22:45.000 --> 00:22:47.000
SCOOPS.

00:22:47.000 --> 00:22:49.000
THERE WAS A BIG EFFORT, IN

00:22:49.000 --> 00:22:50.000
FACT, TO FIND PEOPLE WHO SEEMED

00:22:50.000 --> 00:22:52.000
TO HAVE CREDIBLE EVIDENCE ABOUT

00:22:52.000 --> 00:22:54.000
WHAT WAS GOING ON INSIDE IRAQ.

00:22:54.000 --> 00:22:55.000
BECAUSE, IN FACT, IF YOU COULD

00:22:55.000 --> 00:22:57.000
FIND SOMEBODY WHO WAS CREDIBLE

00:22:57.000 --> 00:23:00.000
TALKING ABOUT A NUCLEAR PROGRAM

00:23:00.000 --> 00:23:02.000
IN IRAQ OR CHEMICAL WEAPONS,

00:23:02.000 --> 00:23:04.000
THAT WOULD BE A BIG STORY.

00:23:04.000 --> 00:23:06.000
Moyers: AND IT WORKED.

00:23:06.000 --> 00:23:08.000
THE "NEW YORKER," "U.S. A.

00:23:08.000 --> 00:23:09.000
TODAY," THE "WASHINGTON POST,"

00:23:09.000 --> 00:23:10.000
THE "NEW YORK DAILY NEWS," THE

00:23:10.000 --> 00:23:13.000
"NEW YORK TIMES."

00:23:13.000 --> 00:23:14.000
AND ON PBS, JUST TWO MONTHS

00:23:14.000 --> 00:23:16.000
AFTER 9/11, "FRONTLINE" AND THE

00:23:16.000 --> 00:23:18.000
"NEW YORK TIMES" TEAMED UP FOR A

00:23:18.000 --> 00:23:20.000
DOCUMENTARY ON THE DEFECTORS.

00:23:20.000 --> 00:23:23.000
CAPTAIN SABAH KHODADA IS A

00:23:23.000 --> 00:23:25.000
FORMER ARMY OFFICER WHO DEFECTED

00:23:25.000 --> 00:23:27.000
FROM IRAQ.

00:23:27.000 --> 00:23:28.000
HE MADE A CRUDE DRAWING OF WHAT

00:23:28.000 --> 00:23:30.000
HE SAYS IS A TERRORIST TRAINING

00:23:30.000 --> 00:23:31.000
CAMP ON THE OUTSKIRTS OF

00:23:31.000 --> 00:23:33.000
BAGHDAD.

00:23:33.000 --> 00:23:35.000
Moyers: THERE WERE CAVEATS.

00:23:35.000 --> 00:23:36.000
AND A FURTHER CAUTION: THESE

00:23:36.000 --> 00:23:38.000
DEFECTORS HAVE BEEN BROUGHT TO

00:23:38.000 --> 00:23:40.000
"FRONTLINE'S" ATTENTION BY ONE

00:23:40.000 --> 00:23:41.000
GROUP OF IRAQI DISSIDENTS, THE

00:23:41.000 --> 00:23:44.000
I.N.C., THE IRAQI NATIONAL

00:23:44.000 --> 00:23:46.000
CONGRESS.

00:23:46.000 --> 00:23:47.000
Moyers: BUT THE CAVEATS

00:23:47.000 --> 00:23:48.000
COULDN'T COMPETE WITH THE

00:23:48.000 --> 00:23:50.000
SPECTACULAR TALES TOLD BY

00:23:50.000 --> 00:23:51.000
DEFECTORS.

00:23:51.000 --> 00:23:53.000
BEFORE THE INVASION THE "NEW

00:23:53.000 --> 00:23:54.000
YORK TIME'S" JUDITH MILLER WOULD

00:23:54.000 --> 00:23:56.000
WRITE SIX PROMINENT STORIES

00:23:56.000 --> 00:23:58.000
BASED ON THEIR TESTIMONY.

00:23:58.000 --> 00:23:59.000
AHMED CHALABI IS A

00:23:59.000 --> 00:24:01.000
CONTROVERSIAL LEADER OF THE

00:24:01.000 --> 00:24:03.000
IRAQI OPPOSITION.

00:24:03.000 --> 00:24:05.000
Moyers: AND STILL ON THE WEB,

00:24:05.000 --> 00:24:06.000
A REPORT ABOUT THE DEFECTORS,

00:24:06.000 --> 00:24:08.000
NARRATED BY JUDITH MILLER AND

00:24:08.000 --> 00:24:09.000
PRODUCED BY "NEW YORK TIMES"

00:24:09.000 --> 00:24:11.000
TELEVISION FOR THE "NEWSHOUR" ON

00:24:11.000 --> 00:24:13.000
PBS.

00:24:13.000 --> 00:24:14.000
WELL, JUDY MILLER HAD BEEN AN

00:24:14.000 --> 00:24:15.000
OLD FRIEND OF CHALABI, DID A LOT

00:24:15.000 --> 00:24:16.000
OF THE STORIES ON CHALABI, WAS

00:24:16.000 --> 00:24:18.000
VERY FAVORABLE TO CHALABI.

00:24:18.000 --> 00:24:19.000
Moyers: JAMES BAMFORD FOUND

00:24:19.000 --> 00:24:21.000
OUT THAT IN 2001, CHALABI HAD

00:24:21.000 --> 00:24:23.000
ARRANGED FOR MILLER TO MEET IN

00:24:23.000 --> 00:24:25.000
THAILAND WITH A DEFECTOR FROM

00:24:25.000 --> 00:24:27.000
IRAQ NAMED AL-HAIDERI.

00:24:27.000 --> 00:24:28.000
SO, AL-HAIDERI WAS IN

00:24:28.000 --> 00:24:29.000
BANGKOK.

00:24:29.000 --> 00:24:30.000
JUDY MILLER FLEW THERE TO

00:24:30.000 --> 00:24:31.000
INTERVIEW HIM.

00:24:31.000 --> 00:24:32.000
THE "NEW YORK TIMES" RAN A

00:24:32.000 --> 00:24:34.000
FRONT-PAGE STORY BASICALLY

00:24:34.000 --> 00:24:35.000
CONFIRMING EVERYTHING THE

00:24:35.000 --> 00:24:37.000
ADMINISTRATION HAD BEEN SAYING

00:24:37.000 --> 00:24:38.000
ABOUT IRAQ.

00:24:38.000 --> 00:24:40.000
Moyers: AL-HAIDERI SAID HE

00:24:40.000 --> 00:24:42.000
WAS A KURD FROM NORTHERN IRAQ.

00:24:42.000 --> 00:24:43.000
HE TOLD MILLER THE IRAQIS HAD

00:24:43.000 --> 00:24:44.000
HIDDEN CHEMICAL AND BIOLOGICAL

00:24:44.000 --> 00:24:46.000
WEAPONS; SOME, MILLER REPORTED,

00:24:46.000 --> 00:24:48.000
RIGHT UNDER SADDAM'S

00:24:48.000 --> 00:24:50.000
PRESIDENTIAL SITES.

00:24:50.000 --> 00:24:53.000
THE STORY SPREAD FAR AND WIDE.

00:24:53.000 --> 00:24:54.000
THE "NEW YORK TIMES" IS

00:24:54.000 --> 00:24:55.000
JUST... REMAINS IMMENSELY

00:24:55.000 --> 00:24:57.000
INFLUENTIAL.

00:24:57.000 --> 00:24:58.000
PEOPLE IN THE TV WORLD READ IT

00:24:58.000 --> 00:25:00.000
EVERY MORNING.

00:25:00.000 --> 00:25:01.000
AND IT'S AMAZING HOW OFTEN

00:25:01.000 --> 00:25:03.000
YOU'LL SEE A STORY GO FROM THE

00:25:03.000 --> 00:25:05.000
FRONT PAGE OF THE DAY'S PAPER IN

00:25:05.000 --> 00:25:06.000
THE MORNING TO THE EVENING

00:25:06.000 --> 00:25:08.000
NEWSCAST AT NIGHT.

00:25:08.000 --> 00:25:09.000
PEOPLE IN GOVERNMENT, OF COURSE,

00:25:09.000 --> 00:25:12.000
READ IT, THINK TANKS, AND SO ON.

00:25:12.000 --> 00:25:13.000
THERE WERE SOME RED FLAGS

00:25:13.000 --> 00:25:15.000
THAT THE "NEW YORK TIMES" STORY

00:25:15.000 --> 00:25:17.000
THREW OUT IMMEDIATELY, WHICH

00:25:17.000 --> 00:25:20.000
CAUGHT OUR EYE IMMEDIATELY.

00:25:20.000 --> 00:25:22.000
THE FIRST WAS THE IDEA THAT A

00:25:22.000 --> 00:25:26.000
KURD, THE ENEMY OF SADDAM, HAD

00:25:26.000 --> 00:25:29.000
BEEN ALLOWED INTO HIS MOST TOP

00:25:29.000 --> 00:25:32.000
SECRET MILITARY FACILITIES.

00:25:32.000 --> 00:25:34.000
I DON'T THINK SO.

00:25:34.000 --> 00:25:36.000
THAT WAS, FOR ME, THE BIGGEST

00:25:36.000 --> 00:25:37.000
RED FLAG.

00:25:37.000 --> 00:25:38.000
AND THERE WERE OTHERS, LIKE THE

00:25:38.000 --> 00:25:40.000
IDEA THAT SADDAM HUSSEIN WOULD

00:25:40.000 --> 00:25:43.000
PUT A BIOLOGICAL WEAPONS

00:25:43.000 --> 00:25:45.000
FACILITY UNDER HIS RESIDENCE.

00:25:45.000 --> 00:25:46.000
I MEAN, WOULD YOU PUT A

00:25:46.000 --> 00:25:48.000
BIOLOGICAL WEAPONS LAB UNDER

00:25:48.000 --> 00:25:49.000
YOUR LIVING ROOM?

00:25:49.000 --> 00:25:51.000
I DON'T THINK SO.

00:25:51.000 --> 00:25:52.000
THE FIRST RULE OF BEING AN

00:25:52.000 --> 00:25:53.000
INTELLIGENCE AGENT, OR A

00:25:53.000 --> 00:25:54.000
JOURNALIST-- AND THEY'RE REALLY

00:25:54.000 --> 00:25:55.000
NOT THAT DIFFERENT-- IS YOU'RE

00:25:55.000 --> 00:25:56.000
SKEPTICAL OF DEFECTORS BECAUSE

00:25:56.000 --> 00:25:57.000
THEY HAVE A REASON TO

00:25:57.000 --> 00:25:59.000
EXAGGERATE.

00:25:59.000 --> 00:26:00.000
THEY WANT TO INCREASE THEIR

00:26:00.000 --> 00:26:01.000
VALUE TO YOU.

00:26:01.000 --> 00:26:02.000
THEY PROBABLY WANT SOMETHING

00:26:02.000 --> 00:26:03.000
FROM YOU.

00:26:03.000 --> 00:26:04.000
DOESN'T MEAN THEY'RE LYING, BUT

00:26:04.000 --> 00:26:05.000
YOU SHOULD BE... JOURNALISTS ARE

00:26:05.000 --> 00:26:06.000
SUPPOSED TO BE SKEPTICAL, RIGHT?

00:26:06.000 --> 00:26:08.000
AND I'M AFRAID THE "NEW YORK

00:26:08.000 --> 00:26:09.000
TIMES" REPORTER IN THAT CASE,

00:26:09.000 --> 00:26:10.000
AND A LOT OF OTHER REPORTERS,

00:26:10.000 --> 00:26:11.000
WERE JUST NOT SKEPTICAL OF WHAT

00:26:11.000 --> 00:26:13.000
THESE DEFECTORS WERE SAYING, NOR

00:26:13.000 --> 00:26:15.000
WAS THE ADMINISTRATION.

00:26:15.000 --> 00:26:16.000
A FORMER TOP IRAQI NUCLEAR

00:26:16.000 --> 00:26:18.000
SCIENTIST TELLS CONGRESS IRAQ

00:26:18.000 --> 00:26:20.000
COULD BUILD THREE NUCLEAR BOMBS

00:26:20.000 --> 00:26:22.000
BY 2005.

00:26:22.000 --> 00:26:23.000
WELL, NOW ANOTHER DEFECTOR,

00:26:23.000 --> 00:26:25.000
A SENIOR IRAQI INTELLIGENCE

00:26:25.000 --> 00:26:27.000
OFFICIAL, TELLS "VANITY FAIR" IN

00:26:27.000 --> 00:26:29.000
AN EXCLUSIVE INTERVIEW THAT

00:26:29.000 --> 00:26:31.000
SADDAM HUSSEIN HAS TRAINED AN

00:26:31.000 --> 00:26:32.000
ELITE FIGHTING FORCE IN

00:26:32.000 --> 00:26:34.000
SABOTAGE, URBAN WARFARE,

00:26:34.000 --> 00:26:36.000
HIJACKING AND MURDER.

00:26:36.000 --> 00:26:38.000
DAVID ROSE WROTE THE STORY, HE

00:26:38.000 --> 00:26:40.000
JOINS US NOW FROM LONDON.

00:26:40.000 --> 00:26:41.000
Moyers: IN "VANITY FAIR'S"

00:26:41.000 --> 00:26:43.000
DAVID ROSE, DEFECTORS FOUND

00:26:43.000 --> 00:26:44.000
ANOTHER EAGER BEAVER FOR THEIR

00:26:44.000 --> 00:26:46.000
CLAIMS.

00:26:46.000 --> 00:26:47.000
THE GLOSSY MAGAZINE, A FAVORITE

00:26:47.000 --> 00:26:49.000
OF MEDIA ELITES, GAVE HIM FOUR

00:26:49.000 --> 00:26:51.000
BIG SPREADS TO TELL DEFECTOR

00:26:51.000 --> 00:26:52.000
STORIES.

00:26:52.000 --> 00:26:55.000
THE TALK SHOWS LAPPED IT UP.

00:26:55.000 --> 00:26:56.000
WHAT THE DEFECTOR, AL-

00:26:56.000 --> 00:26:58.000
QURAIRY, A FORMER BRIGADIER

00:26:58.000 --> 00:26:59.000
GENERAL IN THE IRAQI

00:26:59.000 --> 00:27:00.000
INTELLIGENCE SERVICE, TOLD ME IS

00:27:00.000 --> 00:27:02.000
THAT THESE GUYS-- THERE ARE

00:27:02.000 --> 00:27:04.000
1,200 IN ALL-- AND THEY'VE BEEN

00:27:04.000 --> 00:27:05.000
TRAINED TO HIJACK TRAINS, BUSES,

00:27:05.000 --> 00:27:07.000
SHIPS, AND SO FORTH.

00:27:07.000 --> 00:27:08.000
AS YOU TRACK THEIR STORIES,

00:27:08.000 --> 00:27:10.000
THEY BECOME EVER MORE FANTASTIC,

00:27:10.000 --> 00:27:12.000
AND THEY'RE THE SAME PEOPLE WHO

00:27:12.000 --> 00:27:14.000
ARE TELLING THESE STORIES, UNTIL

00:27:14.000 --> 00:27:16.000
YOU GET TO THE MOST FANTASTIC

00:27:16.000 --> 00:27:17.000
TALES OF ALL, WHICH APPEARED IN

00:27:17.000 --> 00:27:20.000
"VANITY FAIR" MAGAZINE.

00:27:20.000 --> 00:27:21.000
THE LAST TRAINING EXERCISE

00:27:21.000 --> 00:27:23.000
WAS TO BLOW UP A FULL-SIZE

00:27:23.000 --> 00:27:25.000
MOCKUP OF A U.S. DESTROYER IN A

00:27:25.000 --> 00:27:27.000
LAKE IN CENTRAL IRAQ.

00:27:27.000 --> 00:27:29.000
OR JUMPING INTO PITS OF

00:27:29.000 --> 00:27:33.000
FOULED WATER AND HAVING TO KILL

00:27:33.000 --> 00:27:34.000
A DOG WITH YOUR BARE TEETH.

00:27:34.000 --> 00:27:36.000
I MEAN, THE... AND THIS WAS

00:27:36.000 --> 00:27:38.000
COMING FROM PEOPLE WHO ARE

00:27:38.000 --> 00:27:41.000
APPEARING IN ALL OF THESE

00:27:41.000 --> 00:27:42.000
STORIES, AND AS I... AND

00:27:42.000 --> 00:27:43.000
SOMETIMES THEIR RANK WOULD

00:27:43.000 --> 00:27:45.000
CHANGE.

00:27:45.000 --> 00:27:47.000
MUSAWI TOLD US THAT HE HAS

00:27:47.000 --> 00:27:49.000
VERIFIED THAT THIS MAN WAS AN

00:27:49.000 --> 00:27:51.000
OFFICER IN IRAQ'S RUTHLESS

00:27:51.000 --> 00:27:52.000
INTELLIGENCE SERVICE, THE

00:27:52.000 --> 00:27:53.000
MUKHABARAT.

00:27:53.000 --> 00:27:54.000
AND YOU'RE SAYING, "WAIT A

00:27:54.000 --> 00:27:55.000
MINUTE, THERE'S SOMETHING WRONG

00:27:55.000 --> 00:27:58.000
HERE, BECAUSE IN THIS STORY HE

00:27:58.000 --> 00:27:59.000
WAS A MAJOR, BUT IN THIS STORY

00:27:59.000 --> 00:28:01.000
THE GUY'S A COLONEL.

00:28:01.000 --> 00:28:02.000
AND IN THIS STORY THIS WAS HIS

00:28:02.000 --> 00:28:04.000
FUNCTION, BUT NOW HE SAYS IN

00:28:04.000 --> 00:28:05.000
THIS STORY HE WAS DOING

00:28:05.000 --> 00:28:06.000
SOMETHING ELSE."

00:28:06.000 --> 00:28:07.000
THE DEFECTOR IS TELLING

00:28:07.000 --> 00:28:09.000
MUSAWI THAT IN ORDER TO EVADE

00:28:09.000 --> 00:28:11.000
THE U.N. INSPECTORS, SADDAM

00:28:11.000 --> 00:28:13.000
HUSSEIN PUT HIS BIOLOGICAL

00:28:13.000 --> 00:28:15.000
WEAPONS LABORATORIES IN TRUCKS

00:28:15.000 --> 00:28:17.000
THAT THE DEFECTOR TOLD US HE

00:28:17.000 --> 00:28:19.000
PERSONALLY BOUGHT FROM RENAULT.

00:28:19.000 --> 00:28:21.000
REFRIGERATOR TRUCKS?

00:28:21.000 --> 00:28:21.000
YEAH, YEAH.

00:28:21.000 --> 00:28:23.000
AND HOW MANY?

00:28:23.000 --> 00:28:24.000
SEVEN.

00:28:24.000 --> 00:28:25.000
Moyers: LESLIE STAHL AND CBS

00:28:25.000 --> 00:28:27.000
RETRACTED THEIR STORY A YEAR

00:28:27.000 --> 00:28:28.000
AFTER THE INVASION WHEN NEARLY

00:28:28.000 --> 00:28:30.000
ALL THE EVIDENCE PRESENTED BY

00:28:30.000 --> 00:28:32.000
DEFECTORS PROVED TO BE FALSE.

00:28:32.000 --> 00:28:34.000
"VANITY FAIR'S" DAVID ROSE LATER

00:28:34.000 --> 00:28:35.000
SAID HIGH GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS

00:28:35.000 --> 00:28:37.000
HAD CONFIRMED HIS STORIES, BUT

00:28:37.000 --> 00:28:39.000
THESE WERE THE VERY OFFICIALS

00:28:39.000 --> 00:28:40.000
WHO HAD BET ON CHALABI AS THEIR

00:28:40.000 --> 00:28:42.000
FAVORITE MAN O' WAR.

00:28:42.000 --> 00:28:44.000
TO THE KNIGHT RIDDER TEAM IT ALL

00:28:44.000 --> 00:28:46.000
SMELLED OF A CON GAME.

00:28:46.000 --> 00:28:49.000
WHAT HE DID WAS REASONABLY

00:28:49.000 --> 00:28:50.000
CLEVER, BUT FAIRLY OBVIOUS,

00:28:50.000 --> 00:28:53.000
WHICH IS HE GAVE THE SAME STUFF

00:28:53.000 --> 00:28:55.000
TO SOME REPORTERS THAT, FOR ONE

00:28:55.000 --> 00:28:57.000
REASON OR ANOTHER, HE FELT WOULD

00:28:57.000 --> 00:28:59.000
SIMPLY REPORT IT.

00:28:59.000 --> 00:29:01.000
AND THEN HE GAVE THE SAME STUFF

00:29:01.000 --> 00:29:03.000
TO PEOPLE IN THE VICE

00:29:03.000 --> 00:29:04.000
PRESIDENT'S OFFICE AND IN THE

00:29:04.000 --> 00:29:07.000
SECRETARY OF DEFENSE'S OFFICE.

00:29:07.000 --> 00:29:09.000
AND SO, IF THE REPORTER CALLED

00:29:09.000 --> 00:29:12.000
THE DEPARTMENT OF DEFENSE OR THE

00:29:12.000 --> 00:29:14.000
VICE PRESIDENT'S OFFICE TO

00:29:14.000 --> 00:29:16.000
CHECK, THEY WOULD'VE SAID, "OH,

00:29:16.000 --> 00:29:17.000
I THINK THAT'S... YOU CAN GO

00:29:17.000 --> 00:29:19.000
WITH THAT.

00:29:19.000 --> 00:29:21.000
WE HAVE THAT, TOO."

00:29:21.000 --> 00:29:22.000
SO YOU CREATE THE APPEARANCE, OR

00:29:22.000 --> 00:29:24.000
CHALABI CREATED THE APPEARANCE,

00:29:24.000 --> 00:29:26.000
THAT THERE WERE TWO SOURCES AND

00:29:26.000 --> 00:29:28.000
THAT THE INFORMATION HAD BEEN

00:29:28.000 --> 00:29:29.000
INDEPENDENTLY CONFIRMED, WHEN,

00:29:29.000 --> 00:29:31.000
IN FACT, THERE WAS ONLY ONE

00:29:31.000 --> 00:29:32.000
SOURCE AND IT HADN'T BEEN

00:29:32.000 --> 00:29:33.000
CONFIRMED BY ANYBODY.

00:29:33.000 --> 00:29:34.000
AND LET'S NOT FORGET HOW

00:29:34.000 --> 00:29:36.000
CLOSE THESE PEOPLE WERE TO THIS

00:29:36.000 --> 00:29:38.000
ADMINISTRATION, WHICH RAISES THE

00:29:38.000 --> 00:29:40.000
QUESTION: WAS THERE

00:29:40.000 --> 00:29:41.000
COORDINATION?

00:29:41.000 --> 00:29:43.000
I CAN'T TELL YOU THAT THERE WAS,

00:29:43.000 --> 00:29:45.000
BUT IT SURE LOOKED LIKE IT.

00:29:45.000 --> 00:29:46.000
Moyers: THE ADMINISTRATION

00:29:46.000 --> 00:29:47.000
WAS NOW STEPPING UP EFFORTS TO

00:29:47.000 --> 00:29:49.000
NAIL DOWN A TANGIBLE LINK

00:29:49.000 --> 00:29:52.000
BETWEEN SADDAM AND 9/11.

00:29:52.000 --> 00:29:53.000
JOURNALISTS WERE TIPPED TO A

00:29:53.000 --> 00:29:54.000
MEETING THAT SUPPOSEDLY TOOK

00:29:54.000 --> 00:29:56.000
PLACE IN PRAGUE BETWEEN IRAQI

00:29:56.000 --> 00:29:58.000
AGENTS AND THE 9/11 RINGLEADER,

00:29:58.000 --> 00:30:00.000
MOHAMMED ATTA.

00:30:00.000 --> 00:30:02.000
PUNDITS HAD A FIELD DAY.

00:30:02.000 --> 00:30:03.000
HE HAS CONTACTS OUTSIDE IN

00:30:03.000 --> 00:30:05.000
SUDAN AND AFGHANISTAN WITH

00:30:05.000 --> 00:30:06.000
TERRORISTS.

00:30:06.000 --> 00:30:08.000
HE MET... THEY DID INDEED HAVE A

00:30:08.000 --> 00:30:09.000
CONTACT BETWEEN ATTA AND AN

00:30:09.000 --> 00:30:11.000
IRAQI DIPLOMAT.

00:30:11.000 --> 00:30:12.000
Moyers: IN THE "NEW YORK

00:30:12.000 --> 00:30:14.000
TIMES," WILLIAM SAFIRE CALLED

00:30:14.000 --> 00:30:15.000
THE PRAGUE MEETING AN

00:30:15.000 --> 00:30:16.000
"UNDISPUTED FACT."

00:30:16.000 --> 00:30:18.000
HE WOULD WRITE ABOUT THE ATTA

00:30:18.000 --> 00:30:19.000
CONNECTION TEN TIMES IN HIS OP-

00:30:19.000 --> 00:30:21.000
ED COLUMN.

00:30:21.000 --> 00:30:23.000
JUST WEEKS AFTER 9/11, SAFIRE

00:30:23.000 --> 00:30:25.000
HAD PREDICTED A QUICK WAR, WITH

00:30:25.000 --> 00:30:27.000
IRAQIS CHEERING THEIR LIBERATORS

00:30:27.000 --> 00:30:29.000
AND LEADING THE ARAB WORLD

00:30:29.000 --> 00:30:31.000
TOWARD DEMOCRACY.

00:30:31.000 --> 00:30:33.000
BETWEEN MARCH 2002 AND THE

00:30:33.000 --> 00:30:35.000
INVASION A YEAR LATER, SAFIRE

00:30:35.000 --> 00:30:36.000
WOULD WRITE A TOTAL OF 27

00:30:36.000 --> 00:30:38.000
OPINION PIECES FANNING THE

00:30:38.000 --> 00:30:40.000
SPARKS OF WAR.

00:30:40.000 --> 00:30:42.000
AND ON TIM RUSSERT'S "MEET THE

00:30:42.000 --> 00:30:45.000
PRESS," SAFIRE KEPT IT UP.

00:30:45.000 --> 00:30:46.000
BILL SAFIRE, THE DIFFERENCE

00:30:46.000 --> 00:30:47.000
BETWEEN SUFFICIENT PROVOCATION

00:30:47.000 --> 00:30:50.000
AND A PREEMPTIVE STRIKE?

00:30:50.000 --> 00:30:51.000
I DON'T THINK WE NEED ANY

00:30:51.000 --> 00:30:53.000
MORE PROVOCATION THAN WE'VE HAD

00:30:53.000 --> 00:30:57.000
BY TEN YEARS OF BREAKING HIS

00:30:57.000 --> 00:30:59.000
AGREEMENT AT THE CEASE FIRE.

00:30:59.000 --> 00:31:01.000
HE HAS BEEN BUILDING WEAPONS OF

00:31:01.000 --> 00:31:03.000
MASS DESTRUCTION.

00:31:03.000 --> 00:31:05.000
Moyers: IN OCTOBER, HIS OWN

00:31:05.000 --> 00:31:06.000
PAPER RAN A FRONT-PAGE STORY BY

00:31:06.000 --> 00:31:08.000
JAMES RISEN QUESTIONING THE

00:31:08.000 --> 00:31:10.000
EVIDENCE.

00:31:10.000 --> 00:31:11.000
THEN CAME THIS REPORT FROM BOB

00:31:11.000 --> 00:31:12.000
SIMON.

00:31:12.000 --> 00:31:14.000
THE ADMINISTRATION HAS BEEN

00:31:14.000 --> 00:31:15.000
TRYING TO MAKE THE LINK TO

00:31:15.000 --> 00:31:17.000
IMPLICATE SADDAM HUSSEIN IN THE

00:31:17.000 --> 00:31:19.000
ATTACKS OF SEPTEMBER 11, AND

00:31:19.000 --> 00:31:20.000
THEY'VE BEEN POINTING TO AN

00:31:20.000 --> 00:31:22.000
ALLEGED MEETING BETWEEN MOHAMMED

00:31:22.000 --> 00:31:24.000
ATTA, THE LEAD HIJACKER, AND AN

00:31:24.000 --> 00:31:26.000
IRAQI INTELLIGENCE OFFICER IN

00:31:26.000 --> 00:31:29.000
THE CZECH CAPITAL OF PRAGUE.

00:31:29.000 --> 00:31:31.000
IF WE HAD COMBED PRAGUE AND

00:31:31.000 --> 00:31:32.000
FOUND OUT THAT THERE WAS

00:31:32.000 --> 00:31:34.000
ABSOLUTELY NO EVIDENCE FOR A

00:31:34.000 --> 00:31:37.000
MEETING BETWEEN MOHAMMAD ATTA

00:31:37.000 --> 00:31:40.000
AND THE IRAQI INTELLIGENCE

00:31:40.000 --> 00:31:41.000
FIGURE, IF WE KNEW THAT, YOU HAD

00:31:41.000 --> 00:31:43.000
TO FIGURE THAT THE

00:31:43.000 --> 00:31:45.000
ADMINISTRATION KNEW IT.

00:31:45.000 --> 00:31:47.000
AND YET THEY WERE SELLING THE

00:31:47.000 --> 00:31:49.000
CONNECTION BETWEEN AL QAEDA AND

00:31:49.000 --> 00:31:50.000
SADDAM.

00:31:50.000 --> 00:31:52.000
BOB BAER SPENT 16 YEARS AS AN

00:31:52.000 --> 00:31:54.000
UNDERCOVER AGENT FOR THE C.I.A.

00:31:54.000 --> 00:31:56.000
IN THE MIDDLE EAST.

00:31:56.000 --> 00:31:57.000
Moyers: HOW DID YOU GET TO

00:31:57.000 --> 00:31:58.000
BOB BAER, THE FORMER C.I.A.

00:31:58.000 --> 00:31:59.000
OFFICIAL, WHO WAS SUCH AN

00:31:59.000 --> 00:32:01.000
IMPORTANT SOURCE FOR YOU?

00:32:01.000 --> 00:32:03.000
WE CALLED HIM.

00:32:03.000 --> 00:32:06.000
( LAUGHS )

00:32:06.000 --> 00:32:07.000
Moyers: HOW DID YOU FIND HIM?

00:32:07.000 --> 00:32:09.000
DID YOU KNOW HIM?

00:32:09.000 --> 00:32:10.000
I KNEW SOME FRIENDS OF HIS.

00:32:10.000 --> 00:32:12.000
IT WAS... IT WASN'T A PROBLEM

00:32:12.000 --> 00:32:13.000
GETTING HIS PHONE NUMBER.

00:32:13.000 --> 00:32:14.000
I MEAN, ANY REPORTER COULD GET

00:32:14.000 --> 00:32:15.000
HIS PHONE NUMBER.

00:32:15.000 --> 00:32:16.000
Moyers: WHO WAS HE?

00:32:16.000 --> 00:32:16.000
AND WHAT... WHY WAS HE

00:32:16.000 --> 00:32:17.000
IMPORTANT?

00:32:17.000 --> 00:32:19.000
HE WAS ONE OF THE GUYS WHO

00:32:19.000 --> 00:32:20.000
WAS SENT TO PRAGUE TO FIND THAT

00:32:20.000 --> 00:32:21.000
LINK.

00:32:21.000 --> 00:32:23.000
HE WAS SENT TO FIND THE LINK

00:32:23.000 --> 00:32:25.000
BETWEEN AL QAEDA AND SADDAM.

00:32:25.000 --> 00:32:26.000
Moyers: HE WOULD HAVE BEEN A

00:32:26.000 --> 00:32:27.000
HERO IF HE'D FOUND THE LINK.

00:32:27.000 --> 00:32:28.000
OH, MY HEAVENS, YES.

00:32:28.000 --> 00:32:30.000
I MEAN, THIS WAS WHAT EVERYONE

00:32:30.000 --> 00:32:32.000
WAS LOOKING FOR.

00:32:32.000 --> 00:32:33.000
Moyers: BUT THERE WAS LITTLE

00:32:33.000 --> 00:32:34.000
APPETITE INSIDE THE NETWORKS FOR

00:32:34.000 --> 00:32:35.000
TAKING ON A POPULAR WARTIME

00:32:35.000 --> 00:32:38.000
PRESIDENT, SO SIMON DECIDED TO

00:32:38.000 --> 00:32:39.000
WRAP HIS STORY INSIDE A MORE

00:32:39.000 --> 00:32:41.000
BENIGN ACCOUNT OF HOW THE WHITE

00:32:41.000 --> 00:32:43.000
HOUSE WAS MARKETING THE WAR.

00:32:43.000 --> 00:32:45.000
IT'S NOT THE FIRST TIME A

00:32:45.000 --> 00:32:46.000
PRESIDENT HAS MOUNTED A SALES

00:32:46.000 --> 00:32:48.000
CAMPAIGN TO SELL A WAR.

00:32:48.000 --> 00:32:49.000
AND I THINK WE ALL FELT FROM THE

00:32:49.000 --> 00:32:51.000
BEGINNING THAT TO DEAL WITH A

00:32:51.000 --> 00:32:53.000
SUBJECT AS EXPLOSIVE AS THIS, WE

00:32:53.000 --> 00:32:55.000
SHOULD KEEP IT IN A WAY ALMOST

00:32:55.000 --> 00:32:58.000
LIGHT, IF THAT DOESN'T SEEM

00:32:58.000 --> 00:33:00.000
RIDICULOUS.

00:33:00.000 --> 00:33:00.000
Moyers: GOING TO WAR, ALMOST

00:33:00.000 --> 00:33:02.000
LIGHT.

00:33:02.000 --> 00:33:03.000
NOT TO PRESENT IT AS A

00:33:03.000 --> 00:33:05.000
FRONTAL ATTACK ON THE

00:33:05.000 --> 00:33:06.000
ADMINISTRATION'S CLAIMS, WHICH

00:33:06.000 --> 00:33:08.000
WOULD HAVE BEEN NOT ONLY

00:33:08.000 --> 00:33:09.000
PREMATURE, BUT WE DIDN'T HAVE

00:33:09.000 --> 00:33:10.000
THE AMMUNITION TO DO IT AT THE

00:33:10.000 --> 00:33:11.000
TIME.

00:33:11.000 --> 00:33:13.000
WE DID NOT KNOW THEN THAT THERE

00:33:13.000 --> 00:33:14.000
WERE NO MASS... WEAPONS OF MASS

00:33:14.000 --> 00:33:16.000
DESTRUCTION IN IRAQ.

00:33:16.000 --> 00:33:18.000
WE ONLY KNEW THAT THE CONNECTION

00:33:18.000 --> 00:33:19.000
THE ADMINISTRATION WAS MAKING

