CAN ACQUIRE A NUCLEAR WEAPON,

00:41:59.000 --> 00:42:01.000
BUT WE DON'T WANT THE SMOKING

00:42:01.000 --> 00:42:03.000
GUN TO BE A MUSHROOM CLOUD.

00:42:03.000 --> 00:42:04.000
THOSE SORTS OF STORIES, WHEN

00:42:04.000 --> 00:42:06.000
THEY APPEAR ON THE FRONT PAGE OF

00:42:06.000 --> 00:42:07.000
THE SO-CALLED LIBERAL "NEW YORK

00:42:07.000 --> 00:42:09.000
TIMES," IT ABSOLUTELY COMES WITH

00:42:09.000 --> 00:42:11.000
A STAMP OF APPROVAL.

00:42:11.000 --> 00:42:13.000
I MEAN, IF THE "NEW YORK TIMES"

00:42:13.000 --> 00:42:15.000
THINKS SADDAM IS ON THE

00:42:15.000 --> 00:42:17.000
PRECIPICE OF SOME MUSHROOM

00:42:17.000 --> 00:42:18.000
CLOUDS, THEN THERE'S REALLY NO

00:42:18.000 --> 00:42:20.000
DEBATE.

00:42:20.000 --> 00:42:21.000
WE READ IN THE "NEW YORK

00:42:21.000 --> 00:42:23.000
TIMES" TODAY A STORY THAT SAYS

00:42:23.000 --> 00:42:25.000
THAT SADDAM HUSSEIN IS CLOSER TO

00:42:25.000 --> 00:42:27.000
ACQUIRING NUCLEAR WEAPONS.

00:42:27.000 --> 00:42:29.000
DOES HE HAVE NUCLEAR WEAPONS?

00:42:29.000 --> 00:42:31.000
IS THERE A SMOKING GUN HERE?

00:42:31.000 --> 00:42:34.000
"THE SMOKING GUN" IS AN

00:42:34.000 --> 00:42:35.000
INTERESTING PHRASE.

00:42:35.000 --> 00:42:37.000
THEN AS WE SAW IN REPORTING

00:42:37.000 --> 00:42:38.000
JUST THIS MORNING...

00:42:38.000 --> 00:42:40.000
WHAT SPECIFICALLY HAS HE

00:42:40.000 --> 00:42:42.000
OBTAINED THAT YOU BELIEVE WILL

00:42:42.000 --> 00:42:43.000
ENHANCE HIS NUCLEAR DEVELOPMENT

00:42:43.000 --> 00:42:44.000
PROGRAM?

00:42:44.000 --> 00:42:46.000
Moyers: WAS IT JUST A

00:42:46.000 --> 00:42:48.000
COINCIDENCE IN YOUR MIND THAT

00:42:48.000 --> 00:42:51.000
CHENEY CAME ON YOUR SHOW AND

00:42:51.000 --> 00:42:52.000
OTHERS WENT ON THE OTHER SUNDAY

00:42:52.000 --> 00:42:54.000
SHOWS THE VERY MORNING THAT THAT

00:42:54.000 --> 00:42:57.000
STORY APPEARED?

00:42:57.000 --> 00:42:58.000
I DON'T KNOW.

00:42:58.000 --> 00:42:59.000
THE "NEW YORK TIMES" IS A BETTER

00:42:59.000 --> 00:43:00.000
JUDGE OF THAT THAN I AM.

00:43:00.000 --> 00:43:01.000
Moyers: NO ONE TIPPED YOU

00:43:01.000 --> 00:43:02.000
THAT IT WAS GOING TO HAPPEN?

00:43:02.000 --> 00:43:03.000
NO, NO.

00:43:03.000 --> 00:43:03.000
I MEAN...

00:43:03.000 --> 00:43:04.000
Moyers: THE CHENEY OFFICE

00:43:04.000 --> 00:43:06.000
DIDN'T MAKE ANY... DIDN'T LEAK

00:43:06.000 --> 00:43:06.000
TO YOU THAT THERE'S GOING TO BE

00:43:06.000 --> 00:43:08.000
A BIG STORY?

00:43:08.000 --> 00:43:08.000
NO.

00:43:08.000 --> 00:43:09.000
( LAUGHS )

00:43:09.000 --> 00:43:10.000
NO.

00:43:10.000 --> 00:43:11.000
I MEAN, I DON'T... I DON'T HAVE

00:43:11.000 --> 00:43:12.000
THE... THIS IS... YOU KNOW, ON

00:43:12.000 --> 00:43:13.000
"MEET THE PRESS," PEOPLE COME ON

00:43:13.000 --> 00:43:14.000
AND THERE ARE NO GROUND RULES.

00:43:14.000 --> 00:43:15.000
WE CAN ASK ANY QUESTION WE WANT.

00:43:15.000 --> 00:43:16.000
I DID NOT KNOW ABOUT THE

00:43:16.000 --> 00:43:17.000
ALUMINUM TUBE STORY UNTIL I READ

00:43:17.000 --> 00:43:18.000
IT IN THE "NEW YORK TIMES."

00:43:18.000 --> 00:43:20.000
Moyers: CRITICS POINT TO

00:43:20.000 --> 00:43:22.000
SEPTEMBER 8, 2002, AND TO YOUR

00:43:22.000 --> 00:43:24.000
SHOW IN PARTICULAR, AS THE

00:43:24.000 --> 00:43:27.000
CLASSIC CASE OF HOW THE PRESS

00:43:27.000 --> 00:43:29.000
AND THE GOVERNMENT BECAME

00:43:29.000 --> 00:43:31.000
INSEPARABLE.

00:43:31.000 --> 00:43:33.000
SOMEONE IN THE ADMINISTRATION

00:43:33.000 --> 00:43:35.000
PLANTS A DRAMATIC STORY IN THE

00:43:35.000 --> 00:43:37.000
"NEW YORK TIMES" AND THEN THE

00:43:37.000 --> 00:43:38.000
VICE PRESIDENT COMES ON YOUR

00:43:38.000 --> 00:43:39.000
SHOW AND POINTS TO THE "NEW YORK

00:43:39.000 --> 00:43:40.000
TIMES."

00:43:40.000 --> 00:43:41.000
IT'S A CIRCULAR, SELF-CONFIRMING

00:43:41.000 --> 00:43:43.000
LEAK.

00:43:43.000 --> 00:43:45.000
I DON'T KNOW HOW JUDITH

00:43:45.000 --> 00:43:46.000
MILLER AND MICHAEL GORDON

00:43:46.000 --> 00:43:48.000
REPORTED THAT STORY, WHO THEIR

00:43:48.000 --> 00:43:49.000
SOURCES WERE.

00:43:49.000 --> 00:43:51.000
IT WAS A FRONT-PAGE STORY OF THE

00:43:51.000 --> 00:43:52.000
"NEW YORK TIMES."

00:43:52.000 --> 00:43:54.000
WHEN SECRETARY RICE AND VICE

00:43:54.000 --> 00:43:55.000
PRESIDENT CHENEY AND OTHERS CAME

00:43:55.000 --> 00:43:56.000
UP THAT SUNDAY MORNING ON ALL

00:43:56.000 --> 00:43:57.000
THE SUNDAY SHOWS, THEY DID

00:43:57.000 --> 00:43:59.000
EXACTLY THAT.

00:43:59.000 --> 00:44:01.000
WHAT MY CONCERN WAS, IS THAT

00:44:01.000 --> 00:44:03.000
THERE WERE CONCERNS EXPRESSED BY

00:44:03.000 --> 00:44:05.000
OTHER GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS.

00:44:05.000 --> 00:44:07.000
AND TO THIS DAY, I WISH MY PHONE

00:44:07.000 --> 00:44:08.000
HAD RUNG OR I HAD ACCESS TO

00:44:08.000 --> 00:44:10.000
THEM.

00:44:10.000 --> 00:44:11.000
Moyers: BOB SIMON DIDN'T WAIT

00:44:11.000 --> 00:44:13.000
FOR THE PHONE TO RING.

00:44:13.000 --> 00:44:14.000
WHEN YOU SAID A MOMENT AGO WHEN

00:44:14.000 --> 00:44:16.000
WE STARTED TALKING TO PEOPLE WHO

00:44:16.000 --> 00:44:18.000
KNEW ABOUT ALUMINUM TUBES, WHAT

00:44:18.000 --> 00:44:19.000
PEOPLE... WHO WERE YOU TALKING

00:44:19.000 --> 00:44:21.000
TO?

00:44:21.000 --> 00:44:22.000
WE WERE TALKING TO PEOPLE, TO

00:44:22.000 --> 00:44:23.000
SCIENTISTS... TO SCIENTISTS AND

00:44:23.000 --> 00:44:24.000
TO RESEARCHERS AND TO PEOPLE WHO

00:44:24.000 --> 00:44:26.000
HAD BEEN INVESTIGATING IRAQ FROM

00:44:26.000 --> 00:44:28.000
THE START.

00:44:28.000 --> 00:44:29.000
Moyers: WOULD THESE PEOPLE

00:44:29.000 --> 00:44:30.000
HAVE BEEN AVAILABLE TO ANY

00:44:30.000 --> 00:44:31.000
REPORTER WHO CALLED OR WERE THEY

00:44:31.000 --> 00:44:32.000
EXCLUSIVE SOURCES FOR "60

00:44:32.000 --> 00:44:34.000
MINUTES"?

00:44:34.000 --> 00:44:35.000
NO, I THINK THAT MANY OF THEM

00:44:35.000 --> 00:44:36.000
WOULD HAVE BEEN AVAILABLE TO ANY

00:44:36.000 --> 00:44:37.000
REPORTER WHO CALLED.

00:44:37.000 --> 00:44:38.000
Moyers: AND YOU JUST PICKED

00:44:38.000 --> 00:44:38.000
UP THE PHONE?

00:44:38.000 --> 00:44:39.000
JUST PICKED UP THE PHONE.

00:44:39.000 --> 00:44:40.000
Moyers: TALKED TO THEM?

00:44:40.000 --> 00:44:42.000
TALKED TO THEM AND THEN WENT

00:44:42.000 --> 00:44:43.000
DOWN WITH THE CAMERAS.

00:44:43.000 --> 00:44:45.000
Moyers: FEW JOURNALISTS

00:44:45.000 --> 00:44:47.000
FOLLOWED SUIT.

00:44:47.000 --> 00:44:48.000
AND THROUGHOUT THE FALL OF 2002,

00:44:48.000 --> 00:44:50.000
HIGH OFFICIALS WERE REPEATING

00:44:50.000 --> 00:44:52.000
APOCALYPTIC WARNINGS WITH

00:44:52.000 --> 00:44:53.000
VIRTUALLY NO DEMAND FROM THE

00:44:53.000 --> 00:44:54.000
ESTABLISHMENT PRESS FOR

00:44:54.000 --> 00:44:56.000
EVIDENCE.

00:44:56.000 --> 00:44:57.000
FACING CLEAR EVIDENCE OF

00:44:57.000 --> 00:44:59.000
PERIL, WE CANNOT WAIT FOR THE

00:44:59.000 --> 00:45:03.000
FINAL PROOF-- THE SMOKING GUN--

00:45:03.000 --> 00:45:05.000
THAT COULD COME IN THE FORM OF A

00:45:05.000 --> 00:45:07.000
MUSHROOM CLOUD.

00:45:07.000 --> 00:45:09.000
Moyers: COULD MEMBERS OF THE

00:45:09.000 --> 00:45:11.000
PRESS HAVE KNOWN AT THAT POINT

00:45:11.000 --> 00:45:13.000
THAT THE ADMINISTRATION WAS

00:45:13.000 --> 00:45:15.000
EXAGGERATING?

00:45:15.000 --> 00:45:17.000
INDIVIDUALS DID IT.

00:45:17.000 --> 00:45:18.000
THERE WERE SPECIALISTS WHO WERE

00:45:18.000 --> 00:45:19.000
RAISING QUESTIONS.

00:45:19.000 --> 00:45:21.000
AND ONE OF OUR REPORTERS, JOBY

00:45:21.000 --> 00:45:22.000
WARRICK, WROTE A VERY TOUGH

00:45:22.000 --> 00:45:25.000
PIECE ABOUT NOT JUST THE

00:45:25.000 --> 00:45:26.000
DISAGREEMENT, BUT... BUT HOW

00:45:26.000 --> 00:45:29.000
DOUBTFUL IT WAS THAT THESE TUBES

00:45:29.000 --> 00:45:30.000
WERE FOR NUCLEAR WEAPONS.

00:45:30.000 --> 00:45:33.000
IT WAS A ONE-DAY PIECE IN OUR

00:45:33.000 --> 00:45:36.000
PAPER, AND IT WASN'T PICKED UP.

00:45:36.000 --> 00:45:37.000
Moyers: BUT WARRICK'S STORY

00:45:37.000 --> 00:45:39.000
APPEARED ON PAGE 18, NOT PAGE

00:45:39.000 --> 00:45:41.000
ONE.

00:45:41.000 --> 00:45:42.000
THE FRONT PAGE OF THE

00:45:42.000 --> 00:45:43.000
"WASHINGTON POST" OR ANY

00:45:43.000 --> 00:45:44.000
NEWSPAPER IS A BILLBOARD OF WHAT

00:45:44.000 --> 00:45:44.000
THE EDITORS ARE TELLING YOU,

00:45:44.000 --> 00:45:45.000
"THESE ARE THE MOST IMPORTANT

00:45:45.000 --> 00:45:47.000
STORIES OF THE DAY. "

00:45:47.000 --> 00:45:48.000
AND STORIES THAT DON'T RUN ON

00:45:48.000 --> 00:45:49.000
THE FRONT PAGE, THE READER SORT

00:45:49.000 --> 00:45:50.000
OF GETS THAT, WELL, THESE ARE OF

00:45:50.000 --> 00:45:52.000
SECONDARY IMPORTANCE.

00:45:52.000 --> 00:45:53.000
Moyers: HOWARD KURTZ IS THE

00:45:53.000 --> 00:45:55.000
"WASHINGTON POST" MEDIA CRITIC.

00:45:55.000 --> 00:45:57.000
I WENT BACK AND DID THE MATH.

00:45:57.000 --> 00:45:59.000
FROM AUGUST 2002 UNTIL THE WAR

00:45:59.000 --> 00:46:01.000
WAS LAUNCHED IN MARCH OF 2003

00:46:01.000 --> 00:46:04.000
THERE WERE ABOUT 140 FRONT-PAGE

00:46:04.000 --> 00:46:05.000
PIECES IN THE "WASHINGTON POST"

00:46:05.000 --> 00:46:07.000
MAKING THE ADMINISTRATION'S CASE

00:46:07.000 --> 00:46:09.000
FOR WAR.

00:46:09.000 --> 00:46:10.000
IT WAS, "THE PRESIDENT SAID

00:46:10.000 --> 00:46:11.000
YESTERDAY," "THE VICE PRESIDENT

00:46:11.000 --> 00:46:12.000
SAID YESTERDAY," "THE PENTAGON

00:46:12.000 --> 00:46:13.000
SAID YESTERDAY."

00:46:13.000 --> 00:46:14.000
WELL, THAT'S PART OF OUR JOB.

00:46:14.000 --> 00:46:15.000
THOSE PEOPLE WANT TO SPEAK, WE

00:46:15.000 --> 00:46:17.000
HAVE TO PROVIDE THEM A PLATFORM.

00:46:17.000 --> 00:46:18.000
I DON'T HAVE ANYTHING WRONG WITH

00:46:18.000 --> 00:46:19.000
THAT.

00:46:19.000 --> 00:46:21.000
BUT THERE WAS ONLY A HANDFUL...

00:46:21.000 --> 00:46:22.000
A HANDFUL OF STORIES THAT RAN ON

00:46:22.000 --> 00:46:23.000
THE FRONT PAGE, SOME MORE THAT

00:46:23.000 --> 00:46:25.000
RAN INSIDE THE PAGES OF THE

00:46:25.000 --> 00:46:26.000
PAPER THAT MADE THE OPPOSITE

00:46:26.000 --> 00:46:27.000
CASE.

00:46:27.000 --> 00:46:28.000
OR, IF NOT MAKING THE OPPOSITE

00:46:28.000 --> 00:46:30.000
CASE, RAISED QUESTIONS.

00:46:30.000 --> 00:46:31.000
"WAS THIS REALLY TRUE?

00:46:31.000 --> 00:46:32.000
WHAT WAS THE LEVEL OF PROOF?

00:46:32.000 --> 00:46:33.000
DID THE C.I.A. REALLY KNOW?

00:46:33.000 --> 00:46:35.000
WHAT WERE THOSE ALUMINUM TUBES?"

00:46:35.000 --> 00:46:36.000
THOSE STORIES, AND SOME

00:46:36.000 --> 00:46:37.000
REPORTERS WORKED HARD ON THEM,

00:46:37.000 --> 00:46:39.000
HAD A HARDER TIME GETTING ON THE

00:46:39.000 --> 00:46:39.000
FRONT PAGE.

00:46:39.000 --> 00:46:40.000
WHY?

00:46:40.000 --> 00:46:42.000
BECAUSE THEY WEREN'T DEFINITIVE.

00:46:42.000 --> 00:46:43.000
Moyers: BUT WHO DEFINES

00:46:43.000 --> 00:46:45.000
DEFINITIVE?

00:46:45.000 --> 00:46:46.000
REPORTER WALTER PINCUS' SOURCES

00:46:46.000 --> 00:46:47.000
DEEP INSIDE THE GOVERNMENT

00:46:47.000 --> 00:46:49.000
QUESTIONED HOW THE INTELLIGENCE

00:46:49.000 --> 00:46:50.000
WAS BEING USED, BUT HIS STORIES

00:46:50.000 --> 00:46:52.000
WERE MOSTLY RELEGATED TO THE

00:46:52.000 --> 00:46:54.000
BACK PAGES.

00:46:54.000 --> 00:46:56.000
ACROSS THE MEDIA WORLD, THE

00:46:56.000 --> 00:46:58.000
BELLICOSE BUT UNCONFIRMED CLAIMS

00:46:58.000 --> 00:47:00.000
MADE THE BIG HEADLINES.

00:47:00.000 --> 00:47:03.000
THE CAUTIONARY STORIES DID NOT.

00:47:03.000 --> 00:47:04.000
AND I BELIEVE, HONESTLY,

00:47:04.000 --> 00:47:06.000
PEOPLE DON'T HAVE A FEAR OF

00:47:06.000 --> 00:47:08.000
IRRITATING THE WHITE HOUSE--

00:47:08.000 --> 00:47:09.000
CERTAINLY NOT AT THE "WASHINGTON

00:47:09.000 --> 00:47:10.000
POST."

00:47:10.000 --> 00:47:14.000
BUT THEY DO WORRY ABOUT SORT OF

00:47:14.000 --> 00:47:16.000
GETTING OUT AHEAD OF SOMETHING.

00:47:16.000 --> 00:47:17.000
Moyers: ISN'T THAT SUPPOSED

00:47:17.000 --> 00:47:19.000
TO BE SCOOP JOURNALISM?

00:47:19.000 --> 00:47:20.000
WELL, BUT YOU COULD BE WRONG.

00:47:20.000 --> 00:47:22.000
IT'S A TRUISM THAT INDIVIDUAL

00:47:22.000 --> 00:47:24.000
JOURNALISTS, AND, IN FACT, THE

00:47:24.000 --> 00:47:27.000
TOP RANK MEDIA OUTLETS THEY WORK

00:47:27.000 --> 00:47:29.000
FOR, REALLY WANT TO BE AHEAD OF

00:47:29.000 --> 00:47:31.000
THE CURVE, BUT NOT OUT ON A

00:47:31.000 --> 00:47:33.000
LIMB.

00:47:33.000 --> 00:47:34.000
AND IF YOU TOOK SERIOUSLY THE

00:47:34.000 --> 00:47:37.000
WARNING FLAGS THAT WERE PROFUSE

00:47:37.000 --> 00:47:39.000
BEFORE THE INVASION OF IRAQ,

00:47:39.000 --> 00:47:42.000
THAT THE ADMINISTRATION'S STORY

00:47:42.000 --> 00:47:43.000
WAS A BUNCH OF NONSENSE ABOUT

00:47:43.000 --> 00:47:45.000
W.M.D.s, YOU WOULD NOT JUST BE

00:47:45.000 --> 00:47:47.000
AHEAD OF THE CURVE A LITTLE, YOU

00:47:47.000 --> 00:47:49.000
WOULD HAVE BEEN WAY OUT ON A

00:47:49.000 --> 00:47:50.000
LIMB.

00:47:50.000 --> 00:47:51.000
I DON'T THINK THERE WAS

00:47:51.000 --> 00:47:52.000
ENOUGH SKEPTICISM BECAUSE I

00:47:52.000 --> 00:47:53.000
THINK MOST OF US KIND OF

00:47:53.000 --> 00:47:55.000
BELIEVED THAT SADDAM HUSSEIN WAS

00:47:55.000 --> 00:47:57.000
BUILDING BIOLOGICAL, CHEMICAL

00:47:57.000 --> 00:47:58.000
AND PERHAPS EVEN NUCLEAR

00:47:58.000 --> 00:48:00.000
WEAPONS.

00:48:00.000 --> 00:48:01.000
Moyers: ISN'T IT THE ROLE OF

00:48:01.000 --> 00:48:02.000
THE FOURTH ESTATE, THOUGH, TO BE

00:48:02.000 --> 00:48:03.000
CRITICAL OF GROUP THINK?

00:48:03.000 --> 00:48:05.000
IT DEFINITELY IS AND I THINK

00:48:05.000 --> 00:48:06.000
WE IN THE PRESS, WE'RE NOT

00:48:06.000 --> 00:48:07.000
CRITICAL ENOUGH.

00:48:07.000 --> 00:48:08.000
WE DIDN'T QUESTION OUR SOURCES

00:48:08.000 --> 00:48:10.000
ENOUGH.

00:48:10.000 --> 00:48:11.000
WE WEREN'T SMART ENOUGH, WE

00:48:11.000 --> 00:48:12.000
WEREN'T ALERT ENOUGH, WE DIDN'T

00:48:12.000 --> 00:48:14.000
DIG ENOUGH, AND WE SHOULDN'T

00:48:14.000 --> 00:48:17.000
HAVE BEEN FOOLED IN THIS WAY.

00:48:17.000 --> 00:48:19.000
Moyers: EVEN OPRAH GOT IN ON

00:48:19.000 --> 00:48:21.000
THE ACT, FEATURING IN OCTOBER

00:48:21.000 --> 00:48:23.000
2002 "NEW YORK" TIMES REPORTER

00:48:23.000 --> 00:48:25.000
JUDITH MILLER.

00:48:25.000 --> 00:48:27.000
THE U.S. INTELLIGENCE

00:48:27.000 --> 00:48:28.000
COMMUNITY BELIEVES THAT SADDAM

00:48:28.000 --> 00:48:31.000
HUSSEIN HAS DEADLY STOCKS OF

00:48:31.000 --> 00:48:33.000
ANTHRAX, OF BOTULINIUM TOXIN,

00:48:33.000 --> 00:48:35.000
WHICH IS ONE OF THE MOST

00:48:35.000 --> 00:48:38.000
VIRULENT POISONS KNOWN TO MAN.

00:48:38.000 --> 00:48:39.000
Moyers: LIBERAL HAWK KENNETH

00:48:39.000 --> 00:48:40.000
POLLAK.

00:48:40.000 --> 00:48:41.000
AND WHAT WE KNOW FOR A FACT

00:48:41.000 --> 00:48:43.000
FROM A NUMBER OF DEFECTORS

00:48:43.000 --> 00:48:44.000
WHO'VE COME OUT OF IRAQ OVER THE

00:48:44.000 --> 00:48:46.000
YEARS IS THAT SADDAM HUSSEIN IS

00:48:46.000 --> 00:48:47.000
ABSOLUTELY DETERMINED TO ACQUIRE

00:48:47.000 --> 00:48:50.000
NUCLEAR WEAPONS AND IS BUILDING

00:48:50.000 --> 00:48:52.000
THEM AS FAST AS HE CAN.

00:48:52.000 --> 00:48:53.000
Moyers: AND THE RIGHT HAND

00:48:53.000 --> 00:48:55.000
MAN TO AHMED CHALABI.

00:48:55.000 --> 00:48:56.000
AND SO DO THE IRAQI PEOPLE

00:48:56.000 --> 00:48:58.000
WANT THE AMERICAN PEOPLE TO

00:48:58.000 --> 00:48:59.000
LIBERATE THEM?

00:48:59.000 --> 00:49:00.000
ABSOLUTELY.

00:49:00.000 --> 00:49:01.000
IN 1991 THE IRAQI PEOPLE WERE...

00:49:01.000 --> 00:49:02.000
I HOPE IT DOESN'T OFFEND

00:49:02.000 --> 00:49:03.000
YOU...

00:49:03.000 --> 00:49:04.000
Moyers: WHEN ONE GUEST DARED

00:49:04.000 --> 00:49:05.000
TO EXPRESS DOUBT, OPRAH WOULD

00:49:05.000 --> 00:49:07.000
HAVE NONE OF IT.

00:49:07.000 --> 00:49:08.000
I JUST DON'T KNOW WHAT TO

00:49:08.000 --> 00:49:09.000
BELIEVE WITH THE MEDIA AND...

00:49:09.000 --> 00:49:10.000
OH, WE'RE NOT TRYING TO

00:49:10.000 --> 00:49:11.000
PROPAGANDA... SHOW YOU

00:49:11.000 --> 00:49:12.000
PROPAGANDA.

00:49:12.000 --> 00:49:13.000
WE'RE JUST SHOWING YOU WHAT IS.

00:49:13.000 --> 00:49:14.000
I UNDERSTAND THAT, I

00:49:14.000 --> 00:49:15.000
UNDERSTAND THAT.

00:49:15.000 --> 00:49:16.000
OKAY.

00:49:16.000 --> 00:49:17.000
BUT OKAY, YOU HAVE A RIGHT TO

00:49:17.000 --> 00:49:18.000
YOUR OPINION.

00:49:18.000 --> 00:49:20.000
Moyers: CONTRARY OPINIONS

00:49:20.000 --> 00:49:21.000
WEREN'T VERY POPULAR IN

00:49:21.000 --> 00:49:22.000
